\id 1CH 1 Chronicles in Boko, Ross Jones 2/08 
\h 1 Lada 
\toc1 Lada sɛ̃́ia 
\toc2 1 Lada 
\toc3 1Lad 
\mt1 LADA SƐ̃IA 
\imt1 Yã́ pↄ́ kú láɛ bee guuↄ 
\ip Láɛ bee Isailiↄ kua káau yã'òwɛ̃ɛ e wàↄ tàńnↄ zↄↄ ũ Babiloni. Lua gbàgbanaↄ mɛ́ kɛ̃̀. Aa yã́ pↄ́ kú Samuɛli láↄ ń Kíaↄ láↄ guu sɛ̀, ãma lousisiyã mɛ́ gbãanɛ́, ↄ̃ aa gbãakpà Lua ua ń Lua yã́owa. Lua mɛ́ kũ̀ àↄ dɛ Isailiↄ kía ũ ado, kíaↄ dɛ aà zĩkɛnaↄ ũɛ, aamɛ aaì kíablea yã́gↄ̃gↄ̃ aà gɛ̃ɛ ũ. Yã́ bee guu Davidiá kía náaideɛ, ↄ̃mɛ Yelusalɛũ sì, ↄ̃ wɛ̃́lɛpi gↄ̃̀ Lua wɛ̃́lɛ ũ Lua kpɛ́ pↄ́ kú we yã́i. Ɔ̃mɛ kíablea yã́ↄ ń lousisiyãↄ dà Isailiↄnɛ. Kía maapi gaa gbɛa lápi kɛ̃na gbãakpà aà bui pↄ́ aa gↄ̃̀ Yudaↄ bùsu kpalablenaↄ ũↄ yã́wa. 
\ip Lápi daalɛkĩi wà gbɛ̃́ↄ tↄdↄ̀dↄ sɛa za Adamuwa e à gɛ̀ pɛ̀ò Davidiwa (1-9). Bee gbɛa wà Davidi kpalablea yã́ bↄↄlɛkɛ̀ (10-29), ãma wi aà yãkɛaeↄ oo: Aà ɛ̀waasoblea, Saulu aà wɛa, aà kpalablea wɛ̃̀ sopla ń kĩnio Hɛblↄ̃, aà Basɛba sɛa, Abisaloũ fɛlɛaaànↄ ń yãpãleↄ. Lápi Davidi Lua kpɛdↄa Yelusalɛũ sↄukɛa yã́ bↄↄlɛkɛ̀ lↄ: Sua ń Dii kpagoloo Yelusalɛũ, Davidi Isaili zĩgↄ̃ↄ naoa, Levii buiↄ ń sa'onaↄ ń lɛ̀sinaↄ ń bↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ zĩ zɛ́kalɛa. 
\c 1  
\s1 Sɛa Adamu e Ablahaũwa 
\r (Daa 5.1-32, 10.1-32, 11.10-26) 
\p  
\v 1 Adamu, Sɛti, Ɛnↄsi,  
\v 2 Kena, Maalalee, Yɛlɛdi,  
\v 3 Ɛnↄki, Mɛtusela, Lemɛki,  
\v 4 Nↄee ń a nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ Sɛũ ń Haũo ń Yafɛtio. 
\p  
\v 5 Yafɛti nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Gomɛɛ, Magↄgu, Mɛdɛ, Gɛlɛsi, Tubali, Mɛsɛki ń Tilasio.  
\v 6 Gomɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Asɛnazi, Lifa ń Tↄgaamao.  
\v 7 Gɛlɛsi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ɛlisa, Taasisi, Sipi ń Lodanio. 
\p  
\v 8 Haũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Etiopi, Egipi, Libii ń Kanaao.  
\v 9 Etiopi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Saba, Avila, Sabata, Laama ń Sabatɛkao. Laama nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Seba ń Dedão ũ.  
\v 10 Niũlodiá Etiopi buiɛ lↄ. Ɔ̃mɛ dṹnia nɛgↄ̃n tↄde sɛ̃́ia ũ.  
\v 11 Egipi buiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ludiↄ, Anaũↄ, Lɛabaↄ, Nafɛtuↄ,  
\v 12 Patusiↄ, Kasuluↄ ń Kɛlɛti pↄ́ Filitɛ̃ↄ bↄ̀ ń guuↄ.  
\v 13 Kanaa nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ian Sidↄ̃ ũ. Aà bui kĩniↄn kɛ: Iti buiↄ,  
\v 14 Yebusi buiↄ, Amↄle buiↄ, Giigasi buiↄ,  
\v 15 Ivi buiↄ, Aaka buiↄ, Sini buiↄ,  
\v 16 Aavadi buiↄ, Zɛmali buiↄ ń Amata buiↄ. 
\p  
\v 17 Sɛũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Elaũ, Asili, Aapasa, Ludi ń Alaũo. Alaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Uzu, Hulu, Getɛɛ ń Mɛsɛkio.  
\v 18 Aapasa mɛ́ Sela ì, ↄ̃ Sela Ɛbɛlu ì.  
\v 19 Ɛbɛlupi nɛgↄ̃ɛ ì plaɛ. Ado tↄ́n Pɛlɛgi, asa aà gↄↄ ↄ̃ wà kɛ̃̀kↄ̃wa dṹniau. Aà dãuna tↄ́n Yotã.  
\v 20 Yotãpi buiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Alɛmↄda, Sɛlɛfi, Azemavɛ, Yela,  
\v 21 Adolaũ, Uzali, Dikala,  
\v 22 Obali, Abimaɛ, Seba,  
\v 23 Ofii, Avila ń Yobabao. Yotã buiↄn we píi. 
\p  
\v 24 Sɛũ, Aapasa, Sela,  
\v 25 Ɛbɛlu, Pɛlɛgi, Leu,  
\v 26 Selugi, Nakↄↄ, Tela  
\v 27 ń Ablaũ pↄ́ wì mɛ lↄ Ablahaũo. 
\s1 Ablahaũ buiↄ 
\r (Daa 25.12-16, 36.1-19) 
\p  
\v 28 Ablahaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Izaaki ń Isimaɛlao.  
\v 29 An buiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Isimaɛla nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ian Nɛbai ũ. A gbɛa Kedaa, Adibɛɛli, Mibisã,  
\v 30 Misima, Duma, Masa, Adada, Tema,  
\v 31 Yetuu, Nafisi ń Kedemao. Isimaɛla nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn we. 
\p  
\v 32 Ablahaũ nↄ Kɛtula pↄ́ i mɛ́sɛdilɛɛ̀o nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Zimana, Yosã, Mɛdã, Madiã, Isebaki ń Suao. Yosã nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Seba ń Dedão ũ.  
\v 33 Madiã nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Efa, Efɛɛ, Anↄki, Abida ń Ɛlɛdaao. Kɛtulapi buiↄn we ḿpii. 
\p  
\v 34 Ablahaũ nɛ́ Izaaki nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Esau ń Yakↄbuo ũ.  
\v 35 Esau nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ɛlifaza, Leuɛli, Yeusi, Yalaũ ń Kolao.  
\v 36 Ɛlifaza nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Temani, Omaa, Zefo, Gataũ, Kenazi ń Amalɛki pↄ́ a ì ń Timinao.  
\v 37 Leuɛli nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Naata, Zela, Sãma ń Mizao. 
\s1 Sei buiↄ 
\r (Daa 36.20-43) 
\p  
\v 38 Sei nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Lotani, Sobala, Zibɛↄ̃, Ana, Disↄ̃, Ezɛɛ ń Disão.  
\v 39 Lotani nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Oli ń Omaũo ũ. Lotani dãen Timina ũ.  
\v 40 Sobala nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Alavã, Manaata, Ebali, Sefo ń Onaũo. Zibɛↄ̃ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Aya ń Anao ũ.  
\v 41 Ana nɛ́n Disↄ̃ ũ. Disↄ̃ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ɛmadã, Ɛsebã, Ilana ń Kelanao.  
\v 42 Ezɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Bilana, Zaavã ń Akanao. Disã nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Uzu ń Alanao ũ. 
\p  
\v 43 Kía pↄ́ aa kpalablè Ɛdↄũ bùsuu Isaili kíaↄ ãaↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Bɛↄↄ nɛ́ Bɛla, Dinaba gbɛ̃́ɛ.  
\v 44 Kɛ́ Bɛla gà, ↄ̃ Bↄzɛla gbɛ̃́ Zela nɛ́ Yobaba zↄ̃̀lɛ aà gbɛu,  
\v 45 Kɛ́ Yobaba gà, ↄ̃ Temani bùsu gbɛ̃́ Usaũ zↄ̃̀lɛ aà gbɛu.  
\v 46 Kɛ́ Usaũ gà, ↄ̃ Aviti gbɛ̃́ Bedada nɛ́ Adada zↄ̃̀lɛ aà gbɛu. Ɔ̃mɛ zĩblè Madiãↄwa Mↄabu bùsuu.  
\v 47 Kɛ́ Adada gà, ↄ̃ Maseleka gbɛ̃́ Samala zↄ̃̀lɛ aà gbɛu.  
\v 48 Kɛ́ Samala gà, ↄ̃ Leobo pↄ́ kú Uflata saɛ gbɛ̃́ Saulu zↄ̃̀lɛ aà gbɛu.  
\v 49 Kɛ́ Saulu gà, ↄ̃ Akaboo nɛ́ Baalanana zↄ̃̀lɛ aà gbɛu.  
\v 50 Kɛ́ Baalanana gà, ↄ̃ Pau gbɛ̃́ Adada zↄ̃̀lɛ aà gbɛu. Aà na tↄ́n Mɛtabɛli, Malɛdi nɛ́ɛ, Mɛzaaba tↄũnaɛ.  
\v 51 Adadapi gà sↄ̃. 
\p Ɛdↄũ bui dezi káauↄn kɛ: Timina, Alava, Yɛtɛti,  
\v 52 Ɔhↄlibama, Ela, Pinↄ,  
\v 53 Kenazi, Temani, Mibizaa,  
\v 54 Magadiɛ ń Ilaũo. Ɛdↄũ bui dezi káauↄn we. 
\c 2  
\s1 Isaili buiↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Isaili nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Lubɛni, Simɛↄ, Levii, Yuda, Isakaa, Zabulↄni,  
\v 2 Dã, Yosɛfu, Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ, Nɛfatali, Gada ń Asɛɛo. 
\s1 Yuda buiↄ 
\p  
\v 3 Yuda nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ɛɛ, Onani ń Selao. À nɛ́ mɛ̀n àaↄ̃piↄ ì ń Kanaa bùsu nↄɛ Sua nɛ́oɛ. Yuda nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ia Ɛɛ yã́ i ka Diiguo, ↄ̃ à aà dɛ̀.  
\v 4 Yuda mɛ́ Pɛlɛzi ń Zelao ì ń a nɛ́pi gyaao, ↄ̃ aà nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ kɛ̀ píi sↄo. 
\p  
\v 5 Pɛlɛzi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Ɛzↄ̃nↄ ń Amuluo ũ.  
\v 6 Zela nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Zimli, Etani, Emani, Kaloli ń Daadao. Aà nɛ́piↄ kɛ̀ píi sↄo.  
\v 7 Kaami nɛgↄ̃ɛn Akãa\f + \fr 2.7 \ft Yoz 7.1\f* ũ. À yã'ì Isailiↄnɛ, à bↄ̀ Dii yã́ kpɛ à láaipↄ sɛ̀. 
\p  
\v 8 Etani nɛgↄ̃ɛn Azalia ũ. 
\p  
\v 9 Ɛzↄ̃nↄ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Yelamɛli, Laũ ń Kalɛbuo. 
\p  
\v 10 Laũ Aminadabu ì, Aminadabu Yudaↄ kía Naasↄ̃ ì,  
\v 11 Naasↄ̃ Salamↄ ì, Salamↄ Bↄazu ì,  
\v 12 Bↄazu Ɔbɛdi ì, Ɔbɛdi Yɛse ì, 
\p  
\v 13 Yɛse nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ian Ɛliabu ũ, a plaade Abinadabu, a àaↄ̃de Sãma,  
\v 14 a síiↄ̃de Nɛtanɛli, a sↄode Ladai,  
\v 15 a soolode Ozɛũ, a soplade Davidi.  
\v 16 An dãeↄn Zeluia ń Abigailio ũ. Zeluia nɛgↄ̃ɛ àaↄ̃ɛ: Abisai, Yoabu ń Asaɛlio.  
\v 17 Abigaili mɛ́ Amasa ì. Amasapi den Isimaɛla bui Yɛtɛɛ ũ. 
\p  
\v 18 Ɛzↄ̃nↄ nɛ́ Kalɛbu nɛ́ↄ ì ń a na Azubao. Aà nɛnↄɛn Yelio ũ. Aà nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Yesɛɛ, Sobabu ń Aadↄ̃o.  
\v 19 Kɛ́ Azuba gà, ↄ̃ Kalɛbu Ɛflata sɛ̀ à Hulu ìò.  
\v 20 Hulu Uli ì, ↄ̃ Uli Bezalɛli ì. 
\p  
\v 21 Bee gbɛa kɛ́ Ɛzↄ̃nↄ kà wɛ̃̀ bàaↄ̃, ↄ̃ à Makii nɛ́ pↄ́ dɛ Galada da ũ sɛ̀ à Segubu ìò.  
\v 22 Segubupi mɛ́ Yaii ì. Yaiipi wɛ̃́lɛ vĩ Galada bùsuu mɛ̀n bao ń àaↄ̃o.  
\v 23 Ɔ̃ Gesuuↄ ń Alaũↄ lɛ̀lɛ Yaii wɛ̃́lɛpiↄwa ń Kenatio ń a bualoũↄ. Wɛ̃́lɛpiↄ kɛ̀ píi bàaↄ̃. Galada mae Makii buiↄn we píi.  
\v 24 Kɛ́ Ɛzↄ̃nↄ gà Kalɛbu Ɛflata, ↄ̃ aà na Abia Asuli ì. Asulipi mɛ́ Tekoa kàlɛ. 
\p  
\v 25 Ɛzↄ̃nↄ yoa Yelamɛli nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: A sɛ̃́ian Laũ ũ, a gbɛa Buna, Olɛni, Ozɛũ ń Ahiao.  
\v 26 Yelamɛli nↄ pãle vĩ, aà tↄ́n Atala. Ɔ̃mɛ Onaũ da ũ.  
\v 27 Yelamɛli yoa Laũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: A sɛ̃́ian Maaza ũ, a gbɛa Yamini ń Ekɛɛo.  
\v 28 Onaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Samai ń Yadao ũ. Samai nɛgↄ̃ɛn Nadabu ń Abisuuo ũ. 
\p  
\v 29 Abisuu na tↄ́n Abihaili, ↄ̃ à Abani ń Mↄlidio ì.  
\v 30 Nadabu nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Sɛlɛdi ń Apaiũo ũ. Sɛlɛdi gà nɛ́saiɛ.  
\v 31 Apaiũ mɛ́ Isi ì, ↄ̃ Isi Sesã ì, ↄ̃ Sesã Alai ì. 
\p  
\v 32 Samai dãuna Yada nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Yɛtɛɛ ń Yonatãao ũ. Yɛtɛɛ gà nɛ́saiɛ.  
\v 33 Yonatãa nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Pɛlɛti ń Zazao ũ. Yelamɛli buiↄn we. 
\p  
\v 34 Sesã nɛgↄ̃ɛ vĩo, sema nɛnↄɛ. Sesã Etiopi gbɛ̃́ vĩ zↄ ũ, aà tↄ́n Yala.  
\v 35 Ɔ̃ Sesãpi a nɛnↄɛ kpà a zↄ Yalapiwa, ↄ̃ à Atai ìò.  
\v 36 Atai Natã ì, Natã Zabada ì,  
\v 37 Zabada Ɛflala ì, Ɛflala Ɔbɛdi ì,  
\v 38 Ɔbɛdi Yehu ì, Yehu Azalia ì,  
\v 39 Azalia Ɛlɛzi ì, Ɛlɛzi Ɛlasa ì,  
\v 40 Ɛlasa Sisemai ì, Sisemai Saluũ ì,  
\v 41 Saluũ Yekamia ì, Yekamia Ɛlisama ì. 
\s1 Kalɛbu buiↄ 
\p  
\v 42 Yelamɛli dãuna Kalɛbu nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: A sɛ̃́ia Mɛsa mɛ́ Zifi ì, a plaade Malesa mɛ́ Hɛblↄ̃ ì.  
\v 43 Hɛblↄ̃ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Kola, Tapua, Lɛkɛũ ń Sɛmao.  
\v 44 Sɛma Lahaũ ì, Lahaũ Yↄↄkaũ ì, Lɛkɛũ Samai ì.  
\v 45 Samaipi mɛ́ Maↄni pↄ́ Bɛzuu kàlɛ ì.  
\v 46 Kalɛbu mɛ́ Halana ń Mↄzao ń Gazezio ì ń a nↄ Efa pↄ́ i mɛ́sɛdilɛɛ̀oo, ↄ̃ Halanapi Gazezi ì. 
\p  
\v 47 Yadai nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Lɛgɛũ, Yotaũ, Gesã, Pɛlɛti, Efa ń Saafao. 
\p  
\v 48 Kalɛbu mɛ́ Sɛbɛɛ ń Tilanao ì ń a nↄ Maaka pↄ́ i mɛ́sɛdilɛɛ̀oo.  
\v 49 Ɔ̃ à Mademana mae Saafa ìò ń Gibɛa mae Mabenao. Kalɛbu nɛnↄɛn Akesa ũ.  
\v 50 Kalɛbu buiↄn kɛ lↄ. 
\p Aà na Ɛflata nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ia Hulu nɛ́ↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Sobala pↄ́ Kiliayaaliũ kàlɛ  
\v 51 ń Salɛma pↄ́ Bɛtɛlɛũ kàlɛo ń Alefa pↄ́ Bɛgadee kàlɛo. 
\p  
\v 52 Sobala pↄ́ Kiliayaaliũ kàlɛ buiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Aloedeↄ ń Manaata gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ  
\v 53 ń Kiliayaaliũ buiɛ beeↄ: Yɛtɛɛ buiↄ ń Pu buiↄ ń Suma buiↄ ń Misela buiↄ. Zↄladeↄ ń Ɛsɛtaodeↄ bↄ̀ buipiↄ guuɛ. 
\p  
\v 54 Salema buiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Bɛtɛlɛũdeↄ, Nɛtofadeↄ, Atalobɛyoabudeↄ ń Manaata gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ ń Zↄladeↄ  
\v 55 ń lakɛ̃na pↄ́ kú Yabɛziↄ. Aamɛ Tila buiↄ ń Simɛa buiↄ ń Suka buiↄ ũ. Keni buipiↄ bↄ̀ Lekabu buiↄ guuɛ. Amata mɛ́ ń dezi káau ũ. 
\c 3  
\s1 Davidi buiↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Davidi nɛ́ pↄ́ a ì Hɛblↄ̃ↄn kɛ: À a nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ia Aminↄ ì ń Yezɛlɛɛ gbɛ̃́ Ainↄaũoɛ. À a plaade ì ń Kaamɛli gbɛ̃́ Abigailioɛ, ↄ̃n Daniɛli ũ.  
\v 2 À a àaↄ̃de ì ń Gesuu kí Talemai nɛ́ Maakaoɛ, ↄ̃n Abisaloũ ũ. À a síiↄ̃de ì ń Agitaoɛ, ↄ̃n Adonia ũ.  
\v 3 À a sↄode ì ń Abitalioɛ, ↄ̃n Sefatia ũ. À a soolode ì ń a nↄ Egelaoɛ, ↄ̃n Iteaũ ũ.  
\v 4 À nɛgↄ̃ɛ gbɛ̃ↄn soolopiↄ ì Hɛblↄ̃ɛ. À kpalablè we wɛ̃̀ sopla ń mↄ soolooɛ, mɛ́ à kpalablè Yelusalɛũ wɛ̃̀ baakwi ń àaↄ̃o.\f + \fr 3.4 \ft 2Sam 5.4-5, 1Kia 2.11, 1Lad 29.27\f* 
\p  
\v 5 Nɛ́ pↄ́ a ì Yelusalɛũↄ tↄ́n kɛ: À nɛgↄ̃ɛ gbɛ̃ↄn síiↄ̃ɛ beeↄ ì ń Amiɛli nɛ́ Basɛbaoɛ: Simɛa, Sobabu, Natã ń Salomↄↄo.  
\v 6 Bee gbɛa Ibaa, Ɛlisua, Ɛlifele,  
\v 7 Nↄga, Nɛfɛgi, Yafia,  
\v 8 Ɛlisama, Ɛliada ń Ɛlifeleo. Aà nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ kɛ̀ kɛ̃okwin we.  
\v 9 Davidi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn we píi nↄ pↄ́ i mɛ́sɛdilɛ nɛ́oↄ nɛ́ↄ bàasi. An dãen Tamaa ũ. 
\s1 Yuda kíaↄ 
\p  
\v 10 Salomↄↄ Lↄbↄaũ ì, Lↄbↄaũ Abia ì, Abia Asa ì, Asa Yosafa ì,  
\v 11 Yosafa Yolaũ ì, Yolaũ Aazia ì, Aazia Yoasi ì,  
\v 12 Yoasi Amazia ì, Amazia Azalia ì, Azalia Yotaũ ì,  
\v 13 Yotaũ Aaza ì, Aaza Ezekia ì, Ezekia Manase ì,  
\v 14 Manase Amↄ ì, Amↄ Yosia ì.  
\v 15 Yosiapi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: A sɛ̃́ia Yohanani, a plaade Yoakiũ, a àaↄ̃de Zedekia, a síiↄ̃de Saluũ.  
\v 16 Yoakiũ nɛ́ Yɛkↄnia mɛ́ zↄ̃̀lɛ aà gbɛu, ↄ̃ Zedekia zↄ̃̀lɛ Yɛkↄnia gbɛu. 
\s1 Taa ń Yudaↄ Babiloni bùsuu gbɛa kíabuiↄ 
\p  
\v 17 Wà tà ń Yɛkↄniapio zĩ̀zↄ ũɛ. Aà nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Salatiɛli,  
\v 18 Malakilaũ, Pedaia, Sɛnazaa, Yekamia, Osama ń Nɛdabiao.  
\v 19 Pedaia nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Zolobabɛli ń Simɛio ũ. Zolobabɛlipi mɛ́ Mɛsulaũ ń Ananiao ì ń ń dãe Selomio.  
\v 20 À nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ì lↄ gbɛ̃ↄn sↄo: Asuba, Oɛli, Bɛlɛkia, Asadia ń Yusabɛsɛdio. 
\p  
\v 21 Anania nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Pelatia ń Yesaiao ũ. Aà buiↄn Lefaia buiↄ ũ lↄ ń Aanana buiↄ ń Obadia buiↄ ń Sekania buiↄ.  
\v 22 Sekania nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Semaia, Atusu, Igali, Balia, Nɛalia ń Safatao, aa kɛ̀ soolo.  
\v 23 Nɛalia nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ɛlioenai, Izikia ń Azikaũo, aa kɛ̀ àaↄ̃.  
\v 24 Ɛlioenai nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Odavia, Ɛliasibu, Pelaia, Akubu, Yohanani, Delaia ń Ananio, aa kɛ̀ sopla. 
\c 4  
\s1 Yuda bui kĩniↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Yuda nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Pɛlɛzi, Ɛzↄ̃nↄ, Kaami, Hulu ń Sobalao.  
\v 2 Sobalapi nɛ́ Leaia mɛ́ Yaata ì, ↄ̃ Yaata Ahumai ń Laadio ì. Zↄla buiↄn we. 
\p  
\v 3 Etaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Yezɛlɛɛ, Isema ń Ibasio ũ. An dãe tↄ́n Azɛlɛponi.  
\v 4 Ɔ̃ à Penuɛli pↄ́ Gedoo kàlɛ ì ń Ezɛɛ pↄ́ Usa kàlɛo. Ɛflata yoa Hulu pↄ́ Bɛtɛlɛũ kàlɛ buiↄn we. 
\p  
\v 5 Asuli pↄ́ Tekoa kàlɛ nↄ vĩ plaɛ, aan Ɛla ń Naalao ũ.  
\v 6 Naala mɛ́ Ahuzaũ ń Efɛɛo ń Temɛnio ń Aasetalio ì.  
\v 7 Ɛla mɛ́ Zɛlɛti ń Zohaao ń Ɛnanio ì. 
\p  
\v 8 Kozu Anubi ń Zobebao ì. An guu ↄ̃ Aluũ nɛ́ Ahaleli buiↄ bↄ̀u. 
\p  
\v 9 Yabɛsi bɛɛɛ vĩ dɛ a gbɛ̃́ↄla. Aà da mɛ́ tↄkpàɛ̀ Yabɛsi,\f + \fr 4.9 \ft Bee mɛ̀ wãwã.\f* kɛ à aà ì ń wãwã zↄ̃ↄo yã́i.  
\v 10 Yabɛsi wiilɛ̀ Isailiↄ Luawa à mɛ̀: Báaadamagu, ní ma bùsu kã́fĩmɛɛ. Ɔdaa, ní ma bↄ vãiu, kɛ́ másu wãwãmao yã́i. Ɔ̃ Lua sìaànↄ. 
\p  
\v 11 Suha dãuna Kelubu mɛ́ Mɛhii ì, ↄ̃ Mɛhii Ɛsitoni ì.  
\v 12 Ɛsitoni mɛ́ Bɛlafa ń Paseao ń Tehinao ì. Tehinapi mɛ́ Naasa kàlɛ. Lekadeↄn we. 
\p  
\v 13 Kenazi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Ɔniɛli ń Selaiao ũ. Ɔniɛli nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Hata ń Mɛↄnↄtaio ũ.  
\v 14 Mɛↄnↄtaipi mɛ́ Ɔfɛla ì. Selaia mɛ́ Yoabu ì. Ɔ̃mɛ sia pↄ́ kú Siaↄ Guzulɛuↄ dezi ũ. 
\p  
\v 15 Yefũnɛ nɛ́ Kalɛbu nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ilu, Ela ń Naaũo. Elapi mɛ́ Kenazi ì. 
\p  
\v 16 Yalɛlɛli nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Zifi, Zifa, Tilia ń Asalɛo. 
\p  
\v 17-18 Ɛzala nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Yɛtɛɛ, Mɛlɛdi, Efɛɛ ń Yalonio. Mɛlɛdi mɛ́ Falaↄ̃ↄ nɛ́ Bitia sɛ̀, ↄ̃ à Miliaũ ń Samaio ìò ń Ɛsɛmↄa mae Isebao. Aà Yuda nↄ ↄ̃ à Gedoo mae Yɛlɛdi ń Soko mae Ɛbɛɛ ń Zanↄa mae Yekutiɛo ìò. 
\p  
\v 19 Odia na Nahaũ dãe buiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Gaami bui pↄ́ kú Kɛilaↄ ń Maaka bui pↄ́ kú Ɛsɛmↄaↄ. 
\p  
\v 20 Simↄↄ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Aminↄ, Lina, Bɛnana ń Tilonio. Isi buiↄn Zoeti ń aà nɛgↄ̃ɛo ũ. 
\p  
\v 21 Yuda nɛ́ Sela buiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ɛɛ pↄ́ Leka kàlɛ, Laada pↄ́ Malesa kàlɛ ń zwã̀atãnaↄ bui pↄ́ kú Bɛtasebeaↄ  
\v 22 ń Yokiũo ń Kozebadeↄ ń Yoasio ń Salafa pↄ́ aa dɛ Mↄabu bùsu kíaↄ ũↄ ń Yasubilɛmao. Yã́piↄ kɛgↄↄ zi.  
\v 23 Gbɛ̃́piↄá oobonaↄnɛ, aa ku Nɛtaiũ ń Gedelao. We aaì zĩkɛu kíaɛ. 
\s1 Simɛↄ buiↄ 
\p  
\v 24 Simɛↄ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Nɛmuɛli, Yamini, Yalibu, Zela ń Sauluo.  
\v 25 Saulu Saluũ ì, Saluũ Mibisã ì, Mibisã Misima ì.  
\v 26 Misima Amuɛli ì, Amuɛli Zakuu ì, Zakuu Simɛi ì.  
\v 27 Simɛipi nɛgↄ̃ɛ ì gɛ̃o ń mɛ̀ndooɛ, nɛnↄɛ soolo. Aà gbɛ̃́piↄ sↄ̃ aai nɛ'i dasio. Bee yã́i Simɛↄ buiↄ dasi lán Yudaↄwao. 
\p  
\v 28 Wɛ̃́lɛ pↄ́ aa zↄ̃̀lɛuↄn kɛ: Bɛɛsɛba, Mↄlada, Azaasuali,  
\v 29 Bila, Ɛsɛũ, Tolada,  
\v 30 Bɛtuɛ, Ɔↄma, Zikilaga,  
\v 31 Bɛmaakabo, Azaasusiũ, Bɛbili ń Saalaiũo. An wɛ̃́lɛↄn we\f + \fr 4.31 \ft Yoz 19.2-8\f* e à gɛ̀ pɛ̀ò Davidi kpalableawa.  
\v 32 Aa wɛ̃́lɛↄ vĩ mɛ̀n sↄo lↄ: Etaũ, Aini, Limↄ, Tokɛ̃ ń Asão  
\v 33 ń ń bualoũ pↄ́ liaa wɛ̃́lɛpiↄziↄ e à gɛ̀ pɛ̀ò Baalawa. An wɛ̃́lɛↄn we. Aa ń buiↄ tↄ́ dàlau, ↄ̃n kɛ: 
\p  
\v 34 Mɛsoba, Yamɛlɛki, Amazia nɛ́ Yosa,  
\v 35 Yoɛli, Yosibia nɛ́, Selaia tↄũna, Asiɛ sĩ́wɛna Yehu,  
\v 36 Ɛlioenai, Yaakoba, Yesohaia, Asaia, Adiɛli, Yesimiɛ, Benaia  
\v 37 ń Zizao. Zizapi mɛ́ Sifi nɛ́, Aloni tↄũna, Yedaia sĩ́wɛna, Simɛli sↄ̃kpaɛ, Semaia sĩsĩ ũ. 
\p  
\v 38 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ dàda láupiↄ mɛ́ ń bui dↄaanaↄ ũ. An bɛdeↄ dasikũ̀ maamaa,  
\v 39 ↄ̃ aa fɛ̀lɛ gɛ̀ dã́dãkɛkĩi wɛɛlɛi Gedoo bɛ'aɛ oi guzulɛ gukpɛ oi.  
\v 40 Ɔ̃ aa bↄ̀ dã́dãkɛkĩi maa táaedewa we. Bùsupi yàasa mɛ́ a yãkele vĩo. Haũ buieↄ mɛ́ kú we yãa.  
\v 41 Gbɛ̃́piↄ gɛ̀ we Yudaↄ kí Ezekia gↄↄɛ. Aa sì Haũ buipiↄzi ń kpɛ́ↄ guu ń Mɛu bui pↄ́ kú weↄ. Aa ń dɛdɛ míↄ, ↄ̃ aa zↄ̃̀lɛ we aa kɛ̀ ń dã́dãkɛkĩi ũ e ń a gbão.  
\v 42 Ɔ̃ Simɛↄ bui gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa pla ń basↄoↄ lɛ̀lɛ Sei bùsu sĩ̀sĩdewa. Isi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ Pelatia ń Nɛaliao ń Lefaiao ń Uziɛlio mɛ́ dↄ̀aanɛ́.  
\v 43 Aa Amalɛki bui kↄ̃na pↄ́ bↄ̀ yãaↄ dɛ̀dɛ, ↄ̃ aa ku we e ń a gbão. 
\c 5  
\s1 Lubɛni buiↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Isaili nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ia Lubɛni buiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ɔ̃mɛ yoa ũ, ãma kɛ́ à gbadà a mae nawa yã́i,\f + \fr 5.1 \ft Daa 35.22, 49.3-4\f* ↄ̃ aà maepi aà yoakɛzɛ kpà Yosɛfu nɛgↄ̃ɛↄwa, wi aà tↄ́ dalau yoa ũ lↄo.  
\v 2 Baa kɛ́ Yuda gbãa a gbɛ̃́ↄ guu, mɛ́ dↄaana bↄ̀ aà buiↄ guu, Yosɛfu mɛ́ yoakɛzɛ vĩ.  
\v 3 Isaili yoa Lubɛni nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Anↄki, Palu, Ɛzↄ̃nↄ ń Kaamio. 
\p  
\v 4 Yoɛli Semaia ì, Semaia Gↄgu ì, Gↄgu Simɛi ì,  
\v 5 Simɛi Mika ì, Mika Leaia ì, Leaia Baali ì,  
\v 6 Baali Beela ì. Ɔ̃mɛ Lubɛni buiↄ dↄaana ũ, ↄ̃ Asiliↄ kí Pulu aà kũ̀ tàò zĩ̀zↄ ũ.\f + \fr 5.6 \ft 2Kia 15.29\f* 
\p  
\v 7 Beela gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ dàda láu daɛdaɛↄn kɛ: Kí Yeiɛli, Zakali  
\v 8 ń Azaza nɛ́, Sɛma tↄũna, Yoɛli sĩ́wɛna Bɛlao. Aa zↄ̃̀lɛ Aloee ń Nɛboo ń Baali Mɛonao.  
\v 9 Aa zↄ̃̀lɛ gukpɛ oi e aa gɛ̀ nà guwaiwai pↄ́ pɛ̀ Uflatawa, kɛ́ an pↄtuoↄ dasikũ̀ Galada bùsuu yã́i.  
\v 10 Saulu gↄↄ aa zĩkà ń Ageli buiↄ, ↄ̃ aa zĩblèmá aa zↄ̃̀lɛ ń wɛ̃́lɛↄ guu bùsu pↄ́ kú Galada gukpɛ oi píiu. 
\s1 Gada buiↄ 
\p  
\v 11 Gada buiↄ kú ń saɛ Basana bùsuu e à gɛ̀ pɛ̀ Salekawa.  
\v 12 Yoɛli mɛ́ ń dↄaana ũ Basana we, Safaũ mɛ́ aà plaade ũ, a gbɛa Yanai ń Safatao.  
\v 13 An gbɛ̃ↄn kɛ daɛdaɛ gbɛ̃ↄn sopla: Mikaila, Mɛsulaũ, Sɛba, Yolai, Yakã, Zia ń Ɛbɛluo.  
\v 14 Buzu Yado ì, Yado Yesisai ì, Yesisai Mikaila ì, Mikaila Galada ì, Galada Yaloa ì, Yaloa Huli ì, Huli Abihaili ì, Abihaili mɛ́ gbɛ̃́piↄ ì.  
\v 15 Abidiɛli nɛ́, Guni tↄũna Ahi mɛ́ gbɛ̃́piↄ uabele sɛ̃́ia ũ.  
\v 16 Gada buiↄ ku Galada ń Basana bùsu wɛ̃́lɛↄ guu ń Salↄna dã́dãkɛkĩio e a zↄ̃lɛwa.  
\v 17 Wà gbɛ̃́piↄ tↄ́ dàlau Yudaↄ kí Yotaũ ń Isailiↄ kí Yeloboaũo gↄↄɛ. 
\p  
\v 18 Lubɛni buiↄ ń Gada buiↄ ń Manase buiↄ lɛɛ doo gbɛ̃́ gbãa pↄ́ kú zĩ̀ sↄu guuↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bla ń síiↄ̃o ń ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń baswaaↄ̃oɛ (44.760). Wà zĩkaa dànɛ́, aa sɛ̀ngbao ń fɛ̃ndao vĩ, mɛ́ aa ka dↄ̃.  
\v 19 Aa zĩkà ń Ageli buiↄ ń Yetuuo ń Nafisio ń Nↄdabao.  
\v 20 Lua dↄ̀ńlɛ à Ageli buiↄ nànɛ́ ń ↄzĩ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kúńnↄↄ píi, kɛ́ aa wiilɛ̀wa zĩlau yã́i. A sìńnↄ, kɛ́ aa a náaikɛ̀ yã́i.  
\v 21 Ɔ̃ aa Ageli buiↄ pↄtuoↄ nàaa, yiongoↄ ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ blakwi (50.000), sãↄ ń bleↄ ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ ↄ̀aa do ń blakwio (250.000), zàa'ĩnaↄ ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ pla (2.000). Aa gbɛ̃́ↄ kũ̀kũ bɛ̃́ɛ lↄ ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ basↄo (100.000),  
\v 22 mɛ́ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ gàga zĩpi guuↄ dasi, asa zĩpi bↄ̀ Dii kĩ́iɛ. Aa zↄ̃̀lɛ ń gbɛu e wà gɛ̀ Isailiↄ kũ̀kũ tàńnↄ.\f + \fr 5.22 \ft 2Kia 15.29\f* 
\s1 Manase bui pↄ́ kú gukpɛ oiↄ 
\p  
\v 23 Manase buiↄ lɛɛ do zↄ̃̀lɛ bùsupiu za Basana e Baali Ɛɛmↄ ń Seniio ń Ɛɛmↄ gbɛo. Aa dasi.  
\v 24 An uabele káauↄn kɛ: Efɛɛ, Isi, Ɛliɛli, Azeliɛ, Zelemii, Odavia ń Yadiɛlio. Gↄ̃sa gbãa tↄdeↄnɛ, mɛ́ uabeleↄnɛ lↄ. 
\p  
\v 25 Kási aa náai vĩ ń deziↄ Luaɛo, aa gbãsĩkɛ̀ ń bùsupi gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Lua ń mìdɛnɛ́ↄ tã́aↄɛ.  
\v 26 Ɔ̃ Isailiↄ Lua tɛkpà Asiliↄ kí Pulu pↄ́ wì mɛ lↄ Tigela Pilɛsɛɛgu, ↄ̃ Pulupi mↄ̀ Lubɛni buiↄ ń Gada buiↄ ń Manase buiↄ lɛɛ dopio kũ̀kũ tàńnↄ Ala ń Abooo ń Halao ń swa pↄ́ wì mɛ Gozã saɛo. 
\s1 Levii buiↄ 
\p  
\v 27 Levii nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Geesↄ̃, Kɛata ń Mɛlalio. 
\p  
\v 28 Kɛata nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Amlaũ, Isaa, Hɛblↄ̃ ń Uziɛlio.  
\v 29 Amlaũ nɛ́ↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Aalona, Mↄizi ń Miliaũo. Aalona nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Nadabu, Abiu, Ɛleazaa ń Itamaao. 
\p  
\v 30 Ɛleazaa Finɛasi ì, Finɛasi Abisua ì,  
\v 31 Abisua Buki ì, Buki Uzi ì,  
\v 32 Uzi Zelaia ì, Zelaia Mɛlaio ì,  
\v 33 Mɛlaio Amalia ì, Amalia Aitubu ì,  
\v 34 Aitubu Zadoki ì, Zadoki Aimaaza ì,  
\v 35 Aimaaza Azalia ì, Azalia Yohanani ì,  
\v 36 Yohanani Azalia ì. Ɔ̃mɛ Lua gbàgba kpɛ́ pↄ́ Salomↄↄ dↄ̀ Yelusalɛũ ua.  
\v 37 Azalia Amalia ì, Amalia Aitubu ì,  
\v 38 Aitubu Zadoki ì, Zadoki Saluũ ì,  
\v 39 Saluũ Ilikia ì, Ilikia Azalia ì,  
\v 40 Azalia Selaia ì, Selaia Yozada ì.  
\v 41 Kɛ́ Dii tò Nɛbukanɛza mↄ̀ Yelusalɛũdeↄ ń Yudaↄ píi kũ̀kũ tàńnↄ zĩ̀zↄↄ ũ, Yozadapi kú ń guuɛ. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Levii nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Geesↄ̃, Kɛata ń Mɛlalio.  
\v 2 Geesↄ̃ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Libeni ń Simɛio ũ.  
\v 3 Kɛata nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Amlaũ, Isaa, Hɛblↄ̃ ń Uziɛlio.  
\v 4 Mɛlali nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Mali ń Musio ũ.\f + \fr 6.4 \ft Bↄa 6.16-19\f* Levii buiↄn kɛ an dezi káauↄwa: 
\p  
\v 5 Geesↄ̃ Libeni ì, Libeni Yaata ì, Yaata Zima ì,  
\v 6 Zima Yoa ì, Yoa Ido ì, Ido Zela ì, Zela Yealai ì. 
\p  
\v 7 Kɛata Aminadabu ì, Aminadabu Kole ì, Kole Asii ì,  
\v 8 Asii Ɛlikana ì, Ɛlikana Abiasafa ì, Abiasafa Asii ì,  
\v 9 Asii Taatu ì, Taatu Uliɛli ì, Uliɛli Uzia ì, Uzia Saulu ì.  
\v 10 Ɛlikana nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Amasai ń Aimↄo.  
\v 11 Aimↄ Ɛlikana ì, Ɛlikana Zofai ì, Zofai Naata ì,  
\v 12 Naata Ɛliabu ì, Ɛliabu Yeloaũ ì, Yeloaũ Ɛlikana ì, Ɛlikana Samuɛli ì.  
\v 13 Samuɛli nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ian Yoɛli ũ, a plaade Abia. 
\p  
\v 14 Mɛlali Mali ì, Mali Libeni ì, Libeni Simɛi ì, Simɛi Uza ì,  
\v 15 Uza Simɛa ì, Simɛa Agia ì, Agia Asaia ì. 
\s1 Lua kpɛ́ 
\p  
\v 16 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Davidi ń dílɛ Dii kpɛ́ lɛ̀sin gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ ũ kpagolo sua we gbɛaↄn kɛ:  
\v 17 Aaìↄ lɛsizĩ kɛ zwã̀akpɛ pↄ́ wì mɛ Kpaaũkpɛ kpɛɛlɛ e Salomↄↄ gɛ̀ kpɛdↄ̀ò Diiɛ Yelusalɛũ. Aa zĩkɛ̀ a zɛ́wa lá wa dìlɛnɛ́wa.  
\v 18-23 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa zĩpi kɛ̀ↄ ń ń nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Lɛ̀sin dↄaana Emani, Kɛata bui deziↄ tↄ́n kɛ maeↄ ń ń nɛ́ↄ daalɛa Isailiwa: Isaili, Levii, Kɛata, Isaa, Kole, Abiasafa, Asii, Taatu, Zefania, Azalia, Yoɛli, Ɛlikana, Amasai, Maatu, Ɛlikana, Zufi, Toa, Ɛliɛli, Yeloaũ, Ɛlikana, Samuɛli ń Yoɛli pↄ́ Emanipi ìo. 
\p  
\v 24-28 Emani gbɛ̃do Asafa mɛ́ ì lɛsi aà ↄplaai. Aà deziↄ tↄ́n kɛ maeↄ ń ń nɛ́ↄ: Levii, Geesↄ̃, Yaata, Simɛi, Zima, Etani, Adaia, Zela, Ɛteni, Malakia, Baaseia, Mikaila, Simɛa ń Bɛlɛkia pↄ́ Asafapi ìo. 
\p  
\v 29-32 An gbɛ̃́ Mɛlali buiↄ dↄaana Etani mɛ́ ìↄ kú ń ↄzɛɛi. Aà deziↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Levii, Mɛlali, Musi, Mali, Sɛmɛɛ, Bani, Amɛzi, Ilikia, Amazia, Asabia, Maluku, Abadi ń Kisi pↄ́ Etanipi ìo. 
\p  
\v 33 An Levii deeↄ mɛ́ zwã̀akpɛ pↄ́ dɛ Lua kpɛ́ ũ zĩ kĩniↄ kɛ̀ píi. 
\p  
\v 34 Aalona ń a buiↄ mɛ́ ì pↄ́ↄ kpasa sa'okĩiwa ń tulaletikatɛakĩio. Aamɛ aaìↄ luakukĩi zĩ kɛ, aaì Isailiↄ duuna kɛ̃́má lá Lua zↄ̀blena Mↄizi dìlɛnɛ́wa.  
\v 35 Aalona buiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ɛleazaa Finɛasi ì, Finɛasi Abisua ì,  
\v 36 Abisua Buki ì, Buki Uzi ì, Uzi Zelaia ì,  
\v 37 Zelaia Mɛlaio ì, Mɛlaio Amalia ì, Amalia Aitubu ì,  
\v 38 Aitubu Zadoki ì, Zadoki Aimaaza ì. 
\s1 Levii buiↄ wɛ̃́lɛↄ 
\r (Yoz 21.4-39) 
\p  
\v 39 Wɛ̃́lɛ pↄ́ wa kpàmá ń zↄ̃lɛkĩi ũↄn kɛ: Kɛata tↄũna Aalona buiↄ ↄ̃ wà gbɛlànɛ́ káau.  
\v 40 Ɔ̃ aa Hɛblↄ̃ pↄ́ kú Yuda bùsuu blè ń a dã́dãkɛkĩi pↄ́ liaaiↄ.  
\v 41 Ãma wà wɛ̃́lɛpi buaↄ ń a bualoũↄ kpà Yefũnɛ nɛ́ Kalɛbuwaɛ.  
\v 42 Aalona buiↄ mɛ́ Hɛblↄ̃ pↄ́ dɛ misiwɛ̃lɛ ũ blè ń Libenao ń Yatiio ń Ɛsɛmↄao  
\v 43 ń Ilɛnio ń Dɛbiio  
\v 44 ń Asão ń Bɛsɛmɛsio, ampii ń a dã́dãkɛkĩioɛ.  
\v 45 Aa Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ wɛ̃́lɛↄ blè lↄ, Gɛba ń Alemɛo ń Anatoo, ampii ń a dã́dãkɛkĩioɛ. Wɛ̃́lɛ mɛ̀n kuɛ'aaↄ̃piↄá Aalona buiↄ pↄ́ɛ.  
\v 46 Kɛata bui kĩniↄ mɛ́ Manase bui pↄ́ kú bɛ'aɛ oiↄ wɛ̃́lɛↄ blè mɛ̀n kwi gbɛlaa guu.  
\v 47 Geesↄ̃ buiↄ mɛ́ Isakaa buiↄ ń Asɛɛ buiↄ ń Nɛfatali buiↄ ń Manase bui pↄ́ kú Basana bùsuuↄ wɛ̃́lɛↄ blè daɛdaɛ mɛ̀n kuɛ'aaↄ̃.  
\v 48 Mɛlali buiↄ mɛ́ Lubɛni buiↄ ń Gada buiↄ ń Zabulↄni buiↄ wɛ̃́lɛↄ blè daɛdaɛ mɛ̀n kwi gbɛlaa guu.  
\v 49 Ɔ̃ Isaili buipiↄ wɛ̃́lɛpiↄ ń ń dã́dãkɛkĩiↄ kpà Levii buiↄwa.  
\v 50 Yudaↄ ń Simɛↄ buiↄ ń Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ wɛ̃́lɛ pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ sìpiↄ kpàmá lↄ.  
\v 51 Kɛata buieↄ mɛ́ Ɛflaiũ buiↄ wɛ̃́lɛↄ blè lↄ. 
\p  
\v 52 Wà Ɛflaiũ bùsu sĩ̀sĩde misiwɛ̃lɛ pↄ́ wì mɛ Sikɛũ kpàmá ń Gɛzɛɛo  
\v 53 ń Yↄkemaũo ń Bɛtolonio  
\v 54 ń Ayalonio ń Galimↄo, ampii ń a dã́dãkɛkĩioɛ.  
\v 55 Manase bui pↄ́ kú bɛ'aɛ oiↄ mɛ́ Anɛɛ ń Bileaũo ń ń dã́dãkɛkĩio kpà Kɛata bui kĩniↄwa. 
\p  
\v 56 Wɛ̃́lɛ pↄ́ Geesↄ̃ buiↄ èn kɛ: Manase bui pↄ́ kú gukpɛ oi wɛ̃́lɛↄ Golana pↄ́ kú Basana bùsuu ń Asaloo ń ń dã́dãkɛkĩio.  
\v 57 Isakaa bui wɛ̃́lɛↄ Kɛdɛsi, Dabela,  
\v 58 Lamↄtu ń Anɛũo ń ń dã́dãkɛkĩiↄ.  
\v 59 Asɛɛ bui wɛ̃́lɛↄ Masala, Abedↄ̃,  
\v 60 Hukoko ń Leobɛo ń ń dã́dãkɛkĩiↄ.  
\v 61 Nɛfatali bui wɛ̃́lɛↄ Kɛdɛsi pↄ́ kú Galile, Hamↄ, Kiliataiũ ń ń dã́dãkɛkĩiↄ. 
\p  
\v 62 Levii nɛ́ Mɛlali buiↄ mɛ́ gↄ̃̀. Ɔ̃ aa Zabulↄni bui wɛ̃́lɛɛ beeↄ è: Yↄkenaũ, Kaata, Limↄnↄ ń Tabooo, ampii ń a dã́dãkɛkĩiↄ.  
\v 63 Aa Lubɛni bui pↄ́ kú Yuudɛ̃ baa bↄaa ń Yelikooↄ wɛ̃́lɛɛ beeↄ è lↄ: Bɛzɛɛ pↄ́ kú guwaiwaiu, Yaza,  
\v 64 Kedemↄ ń Mɛfaao, ampii ń a dã́dãkɛkĩiↄ.  
\v 65 Aa Gada bui wɛ̃́lɛɛ beeↄ è lↄ: Lamↄtu pↄ́ kú Galada bùsuu, Maanaiũ,  
\v 66 Ɛsɛbↄ̃ ń Yazɛɛo, ampii ń a dã́dãkɛkĩiↄ. 
\c 7  
\s1 Isakaa buiↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Isakaa nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ síiↄ̃ɛ: Tola, Pua, Yasubu ń Simɛlↄnio.  
\v 2 Tola nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Uzi, Lefaia, Yeliɛ, Yamai, Ibisaũ ń Samuɛlio. Uabeleↄnɛ ḿpii. Davidi gↄↄ Tola bui gↄ̃sa pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ dàlauↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bao ń plao ń ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃oɛ (22.600). 
\p  
\v 3 Uzi mɛ́ Izilahia ì. Izilahia nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Mikaila, Obadia, Yoɛli ń Isiao ũ. An gbɛ̃ↄn sↄo píiá uabeleↄnɛ.  
\v 4 An bui zĩgↄ̃ pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ dàlau daɛdaɛↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ baakwi ń soolooɛ (36.000), kɛ́ an nↄↄ ń ń nɛ́ↄ dasi yã́i. 
\p  
\v 5 Isakaa bui gↄ̃sa pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ dàlauↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ basiiↄ̃ ń soplaoɛ (87.000). 
\s1 Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ 
\p  
\v 6 Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ àaↄ̃ɛ: Bɛla, Bɛkɛɛ ń Yediaɛo.  
\v 7 Bɛla nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ sↄoɛ: Ɛzɛbↄ̃, Uzi, Uziɛli, Yelimↄ ń Ilio. Uabeleↄnɛ ḿpii. An bui gↄ̃sa pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ dàlauↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bao n plao ń baakwi ń síiↄ̃oɛ (22.034). 
\p  
\v 8 Bɛkɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Zemila, Yoasi, Ɛliɛzɛɛ, Ɛlioenai, Ɔmɛli, Yelemↄ, Abia, Anato ń Alemɛo. Bɛkɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn we píi.  
\v 9 Wà ń uabeleↄ tↄ́ dàlau, mɛ́ an gↄ̃saↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bao ń ↄ̀aa dooɛ (20.200). 
\p  
\v 10 Yediaɛ mɛ́ Bilana ì. Bilana nɛ́ↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Yeusi, Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ, Ehudu, Kenaana, Zetã, Taasisi ń Aisahaao.  
\v 11 Yediaɛ buipiↄá uabeleↄnɛ ḿpii. An bui gↄ̃sa pↄ́ aaì bↄ gɛ́ zĩkaiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ gɛ̃o ń plao ń ↄ̀aa dooɛ (17.200).  
\v 12 Supiũ ń Hupiũoá Ili buiↄnɛ, mɛ́ Husiũá Ahee buiↄnɛ. 
\s1 Nɛfatali buiↄ 
\p  
\v 13 Bila nɛ́ Nɛfatali nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Yaziɛli, Guni, Yezɛɛ ń Sileũo. 
\s1 Manase buiↄ 
\p  
\v 14 Manase nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: À Asiɛli ń Makiio ì ń Sili bui nↄ pↄ́ i mɛ́sɛdilɛɛ̀ooɛ. Makii mɛ́ Galada ì.  
\v 15 Makii nↄsɛ̀ Hupiũɛ ń Supiũo. Aà dãe tↄ́n Maaka. Makii buie tↄ́n Zelofada. Nɛnↄɛↄ a ì atɛ̃ɛ. 
\p  
\v 16 Makii nɛgↄ̃ɛ ì ń a na Maakao, ↄ̃ à tↄkpàɛ̀ Pɛlɛsi. Aà dãuna tↄ́n Sɛlɛsi, aà nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Ulaũ ń Lakɛũo ũ.  
\v 17 Ulaũ mɛ́ Bedã ì. Makii nɛ́ Galada, Manase tↄũna nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn we. 
\p  
\v 18 Aà dãe Amↄlɛkɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Isodo, Abiɛzɛɛ ń Malao ũ.  
\v 19 Semida nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Ahiana, Sikɛũ, Liki ń Aniaũo ũ. 
\s1 Ɛflaiũ buiↄ 
\p  
\v 20 Ɛflaiũ Sutɛla ì, Sutɛla Bɛlɛdi ì, Bɛlɛdi Taatu ì, Taatu Ɛlada ì, Ɛlada Taatu ì,  
\v 21 Taatu Zabada ì, Zabada Sutɛla ì. Ezɛɛ ń Ɛladuo gɛ̀ Gatadeↄ pↄtuoↄ kṹkũi, ↄ̃ wà ń dɛdɛ we.  
\v 22 An mae Ɛflaiũ pↄsia kɛ̀ ń gaa yã́ musu à gↄↄplakɛ̀, ↄ̃ aà daɛↄ mↄ̀ aà nↄ̀sɛ nìniɛ̀.  
\v 23 Kɛ́ Ɛflaiũpi ɛ̀a wùlɛ ń a nao, ↄ̃ à nↄsì à nɛgↄ̃ɛ ì lↄ. Ɔ̃ à tↄkpàɛ̀ Bɛlia,\f + \fr 7.23 \ft Bee mɛ̀ yã'ↄ̃ma guu.\f* kɛ́ yã'ↄ̃ma aà bɛdeↄ lè yã́i.  
\v 24 Aà nɛnↄɛ tↄ́n Sɛɛla. Ɔ̃mɛ Bɛtoloni Musu ń Bɛtoloni Zĩ́lɛo kàlɛ ń Uzɛni Sɛɛlao. 
\p  
\v 25 Lɛfa Lɛsɛfa ì, Lɛsɛfa Tɛla ì, Tɛla Taani ì,  
\v 26 Taani Ladã ì, Ladã Amihudu ì, Amihudu Ɛlisama ì,  
\v 27 Ɛlisama Nuni ì, Nuni Yozuee ì. 
\p  
\v 28 An bùsu wɛ̃́lɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Bɛtɛli ń a bualoũↄ, Naalana pↄ́ kú gukpɛ oi, Gɛzɛɛ pↄ́ kú bɛ'aɛ oi ń a bualoũↄ, Sikɛũ ń a bualoũↄ e à gɛ̀ pɛ̀ Aya ń a bualoũↄwa.  
\v 29 Bɛtɛsã ń Taanakio ń Mɛgidoo ń Dooo, ampii ń a bualoũↄ ku Manase buiↄ bùsuuɛ, ↄ̃ Isaili nɛ́ Yosɛfu buipiↄ ku wɛ̃́lɛpiↄ guu. 
\s1 Asɛɛ buiↄ 
\p  
\v 30 Asɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Imɛna, Iseva, Isevi ń Bɛliao. An dãen Sela ũ.  
\v 31 Bɛlia nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ɛbɛɛ ń Biizai mae Malakiɛo.  
\v 32 Ɛbɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Yaflɛti, Somɛɛ ń Otaũo. An dãen Sua ũ.  
\v 33 Yaflɛti nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Pasaki, Bimali ń Asevao.  
\v 34 Somɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ahi, Lↄga, Uba ń Alaũo.  
\v 35 Aà dãuna Otaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Zofa, Imɛna, Selɛsi ń Amaluo.  
\v 36 Zofa nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Sua, Aanɛfɛɛ, Suali, Beli, Imla,  
\v 37 Bɛzɛɛ, Odo, Sãma, Silesa, Yɛtɛɛ ń Beelao.  
\v 38 Yɛtɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Yefũnɛ, Pisipa ń Elao.  
\v 39 Ula nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ala, Aniɛli ń Liziao. 
\p  
\v 40 Asɛɛ buiↄn we, mɛ́ uabeleↄnɛ ḿpii. Gↄ̃sa gbãa tↄdeↄnɛ mɛ́ dↄaana maaↄnɛ. An zĩgↄ̃ pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ dàlauↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ baasↄo ń mɛ̀ndooɛ (26.000). 
\c 8  
\s1 Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ian Bɛla ũ, a plaade Asebe, a àaↄ̃de Ahala,  
\v 2 a síiↄ̃de Nↄha, a sↄode Lafa.  
\v 3 Bɛla nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Adaa, Ehudu mae Gela,  
\v 4 Abisua, Naamani, Ahoa,  
\v 5 Gela, Sefufã ń Hulaũo.  
\v 6-7 Ehudu nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Naamani, Ahia ń Gelao. Gelapi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Uza ń Aihuduo ũ. Uabeleↄn ń ũ Gɛba, ↄ̃ Gela tò aa fɛ̀lɛ tà Manaata. 
\p  
\v 8 Saalaiũ a naↄ Husiũ ń Baalao yà, ↄ̃ à nɛ́ɛ beeↄ ì Mↄabu bùsuu  
\v 9 ń a na Odɛsio: Yobaba, Zibia, Mɛsa, Malekaũ,  
\v 10 Yeuzi, Sakia ń Miimao. Aà nɛ́piↄn we, ampii uabeleↄnɛ.  
\v 11 À Abitubu ń Ɛlipaao ì ń a na Husiũpio zadↄ̃ i aà yao.  
\v 12 Ɛlipaa nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ɛbɛlu, Misaũ ń Sɛmɛdi pↄ́ Onↄ ń Lodio kàlɛ ń a bualoũↄ. 
\p  
\v 13 À Bɛlia ń Sɛmao ì lↄ. Uabeleↄn ń ũ Ayaloni. Aamɛ Gatadeↄ yà.  
\v 14-16 Bɛlia nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Ahio, Sasaki, Yelemↄ, Zebadia, Alade, Edɛɛ, Mikaila, Isepa ń Yohao. 
\p  
\v 17-18 Ɛlipaa nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Zebadia, Mɛsulaũ, Iziki, Ɛbɛɛ, Isimɛlai, Izilia ń Yobabao.  
\v 19-21 Simɛi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Yakiũ, Zikeli, Zabedi, Ɛlienai, Ziletai, Ɛliɛli, Adaia, Bɛlaia ń Simɛlao. 
\p  
\v 22-25 Sasaki nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Isepã, Ɛbɛlu, Ɛliɛli, Abedↄ̃, Zikeli, Anana, Anania, Elaũ, Anɛtotia, Ifedea ń Penuɛlio. 
\p  
\v 26-27 Yeloaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Samɛselai, Sealia, Atalia, Yaalɛsia, Ɛlia ń Zikelio. 
\p  
\v 28 Wà gbɛ̃́piↄ tↄ́ dàlau. Uabeleↄnɛ ḿpii. Aa kú ń gbɛ̃́ↄ saɛ Yelusalɛũɛ. 
\s1 Saulu buiↄ 
\p  
\v 29 Kɛ́ Yeiɛli Gabaↄ̃ↄ kàlɛ, ↄ̃ a ku we. Aà na tↄ́n Maaka.  
\v 30 Aà nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ian Abedↄ̃ ũ. A gbɛa Zuu, Kisi, Baali, Nɛɛ, Nadabu,  
\v 31 Gedoo, Ahio, Zekɛɛ  
\v 32 ń Simɛa mae Mikeloo. Aa kú ń gbɛ̃́ↄ saɛ Yelusalɛũɛ. 
\p  
\v 33 Nɛɛ Kisi ì, Kisi Saulu ì, Saulu Yonatãa ì ń Malakisuao ń Abinadabuo ń Isibosɛo.  
\v 34 Yonatãa mɛ́ Mika mae Mɛfibosɛ ì.  
\v 35 Mikapi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Pitↄ̃, Mɛlɛki, Talea ń Aazao. 
\p  
\v 36 Aaza Yoada ì, Yoada Alemɛ ì ń Azemavɛo ń Zimlio. Zimli Mↄza ì,  
\v 37 Mↄza Binɛa ì, Binɛa Lafa ì, Lafa Ɛlasa ì, Ɛlasa Aseli ì. 
\p  
\v 38 Aseli nɛgↄ̃ɛ ì sooloɛ. An tↄ́n kɛ: Azikaũ, Bokelu, Isimaɛla, Sealia, Obadia ń Ananio. Aseli nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn we píi.  
\v 39 Aà gbɛ̃do Ɛsɛki nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Aà nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ian Ulaũ ũ, a plaade Yeusi, a àaↄ̃de Ɛlifele.  
\v 40 Ulaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄá gↄ̃sa gbãa kàdↄ̃naↄnɛ. Aa nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ń tↄũnaↄ vĩ dasi, aa kà basoplakwi. 
\p Gbɛ̃́piↄá Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄnɛ ḿpii. 
\c 9  
\s1 Yuda pↄ́ aa sù ń Babɛlioↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Wà Isailiↄ tↄ́ dà Isaili kíaↄ ladau ḿpiiɛ. 
\p Wà Yudaↄ kũ̀kũ tàńnↄ Babɛli, kɛ́ aa bↄ̀ Lua kpɛ yã́i.  
\v 2 Sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ ń Lua ua zĩkɛnaↄ ń Isaili kĩniↄ mɛ́ ɛ̀a sù ń bùsuu ń ń wɛ̃́lɛↄ guuo káau. 
\p  
\v 3 Yuda buiↄ ń Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ ń Ɛflaiũ buiↄ ń Manase bui pↄ́ sù Yelusalɛũↄn\f + \fr 9.3 \ft Ɛza 2.1\f* kɛ: 
\p  
\v 4 Amihudu nɛ́ Utai, Ɔmɛli tↄũna, Imɛli sĩ́wɛna, Bani sↄ̃kpaɛ mɛ́ Yuda nɛ́ Pɛlɛzi buiↄ dↄaana ũ.  
\v 5 Asaia ń a dãunaↄ mɛ́ Yuda nɛ́ Sɛla buiↄ dↄaanaↄ ũ.  
\v 6 Yeuɛli mɛ́ Yuda nɛ́ Zela buiↄ dↄaana ũ. Yuda buipiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń basiiↄ̃kwioɛ (690). 
\p  
\v 7 Mɛsulaũ nɛ́ Salu, Odavia tↄũna, Asenua sĩ́wɛna mɛ́ Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ dↄaana ũ  
\v 8 ń Yeloaũ nɛ́ Ibinɛiao ń Uzi nɛ́ Ela, Mikeli tↄũnao ń Sefatia nɛ́ Mɛsulaũ, Leuɛli tↄũna, Ibinia sĩ́wɛnao.  
\v 9 Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ bui pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ dàlauↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa síiↄ̃ ń basoplakwi ń soolooɛ (956). Uabeleↄnɛ ḿpii. 
\p  
\v 10 Yedaia ń Yoialibuo ń Yakɛ̃o mɛ́ sa'onaↄ dↄaanaↄ ũ  
\v 11 ń Lua kpɛ́ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ Azalia, Ilikia nɛ́, Mɛsulaũ tↄũna, Zadoki sĩ́wɛna, Mɛlaio sↄ̃kpaɛ, Aitubu sĩsĩo  
\v 12 ń Yeloaũ nɛ́ Adaia, Pasuu tↄũna, Malakia sĩ́wɛnao ń Adiɛli nɛ́ Maasai, Yazela tↄũna, Mɛsulaũ sĩ́wɛna, Mɛsilemi sↄ̃kpaɛ, Imɛɛ sĩsĩo.  
\v 13 Sa'on uabeleↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa swaaↄ̃ ń baswaaↄ̃oɛ (1.760). Gↄ̃sa gbãaↄnɛ, Lua ua zĩkɛnaↄnɛ. 
\p  
\v 14 Mɛlali bui Asubu nɛ́ Semaia, Azikaũ tↄũna, Asabia sĩ́wɛna mɛ́ Levii buiↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ  
\v 15 ń Bakebakaao ń Ɛlɛsio ń Galalio ń Mika nɛ́ Matania, Zikeli tↄũna, Bɛlɛkia sĩ́wɛnao  
\v 16 ń Semaia nɛ́ Obadia, Galali tↄũna, Yedutu sĩ́wɛnao ń Asa nɛ́ Bɛlɛkia, Ɛlikana pↄ́ kú Nɛtofa tↄũnao. 
\p  
\v 17 Bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Saluũ, Akubu, Talemↄ, Aimani ń ń gbɛ̃́ↄ. Saluũ mɛ́ ń gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ.  
\v 18 Ɔ̃mɛ ìↄ Kí Bĩ́ibↄlɛ pↄ́ kú gukpɛ oi dↄ̃́a e ń a gbão. Gbɛ̃́piↄ mɛ́ Levii buiↄ fã́ani bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ũ.  
\v 19 Kole nɛ́ Saluũ, Abiasafa tↄũna, Kole sĩ́wɛna ń a gbɛ̃́ Kole buiↄ mɛ́ Lua kpɛ́ kpɛɛlɛ dↄ̃̀anaↄ ũ lá ń deziↄ dɛ Dii bòo bↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ũ yãawa.  
\v 20 Ɛleazaa nɛ́ Finɛasi mɛ́ ń dↄaana ũ gↄↄ bee, mɛ́ Dii kuaànↄ.  
\v 21 Mɛsɛlɛmia nɛ́ Zakali mɛ́ Kpaaũkpɛ bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃ana ũ. 
\p  
\v 22 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wà ń sɛ́ bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ũↄ píi gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń kuɛplaoɛ (212). An tↄ́ↄ ku taalau ń wɛ̃́lɛↄ guu. Davidi ń gu'ena Samuɛlio mɛ́ zĩ gbiapi dà ń deziↄnɛ.  
\v 23 Ampiↄ ń ń buiↄ mɛ́ Dii ua bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ũ.  
\v 24 Aaìↄ zɛzɛa kpɛ́pi gola síiↄ̃ↄwa, gukpɛ, bɛ'aɛ, gugbãntoo ń gɛↄmidↄkĩio.  
\v 25 Zĩeↄ an gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa ku wɛ̃́lɛ ń wɛ̃́lɛoↄ ìↄ mↄ zĩkɛińnↄ gↄↄ soplapla.  
\v 26 Zĩpiá bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn síiↄ̃piↄ yã́ɛ. Levii buipiↄ mɛ́ ì Lua ua kpɛ́nɛↄ ń a làasiↄ dↄ̃́a.  
\v 27 Aaì zɛzɛ lia Lua uai gwã́, aaìↄ dↄ̃́a. Ampiↄ mɛ́ aaìↄ a zɛ́ kili kũa, aaìↄ wɛ̃ lá gu lɛ́ dↄ. 
\p  
\v 28 An gbɛ̃eↄ ìↄ laaidↄ Lua ua zĩkɛbↄↄwa. Tó wà gɛ̃̀ò ge tó wà bↄ̀ò, aamɛ aaìↄ nao.  
\v 29 Wà ń gbɛ̃eↄ dìlɛ aaↄ laaidↄ Lua kpɛ́ kpɛɛlɛ pↄ́ↄ ń a zĩkɛbↄↄwa ń pↄ́wɛntio ń vɛ̃ɛo ń nísio ń tulaletio ń pↄ́ gĩnanaↄ.  
\v 30 Sa'onaeↄ mɛ́ aaì pↄ́ gĩnanapiↄ yãalɛkↄ̃u.  
\v 31 Pɛ̃ɛkɛa\f + \fr 9.31 \ft Lev 2.4-6\f* mɛ́ Levii nɛ́ Kole bui Saluũ nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ia Matitia zĩ ũ.  
\v 32 Aà gbɛ̃́ Kole buieↄ mɛ́ aaìↄ pɛ̃ɛ pↄ́ wì kálɛ dↄ̀ↄdↄↄ kã́mabogↄↄzĩ kɛ.\f + \fr 9.32 \ft Lev 24.5-9\f* 
\p  
\v 33 Levii bui uabele lɛ̀sinaↄ mɛ́ aaìↄ ku Lua ua kpɛ́nɛↄ guu. Wìli zĩ pãle danɛ́o, asa aaìↄ ń zĩ kɛ fãanɛ ń gwãasĩnaoɛ.  
\v 34 Ampiↄ mɛ́ Levii bui uabele pↄ́ kú Yelusalɛũↄ ũ, gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ dàlauↄ ũ. 
\s1 Saulu buiↄ 
\p  
\v 35 Yeiɛli mɛ́ Gabaↄ̃ↄ kàlɛ, ↄ̃ a ku we. Aà na tↄ́n Maaka.  
\v 36 Aà yoan Abedↄ̃ ũ. A gbɛa Zuu, Kisi, Baali, Nɛɛ, Nadabu,  
\v 37 Gedoo, Ahio, Zakali  
\v 38 ń Simɛa mae Mikeloo. Aa kú ń gbɛ̃́ↄ saɛ Yelusalɛũɛ. 
\p  
\v 39 Nɛɛ Kisi ì, Kisi Saulu ì, Saulu Yonatãa ì ń Malakisuao ń Abinadabuo ń Isibosɛo.  
\v 40 Yonatãa mɛ́ Mika mae Mɛfibosɛ ì.  
\v 41 Mikapi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Pitↄ̃, Mɛlɛki, Talea ń Aazao.  
\v 42 Aaza Yada ì, Yala Alemɛ ì ń Azemavɛo ń Zimlio. Zimli Mↄza ì,  
\v 43 Mↄza Binɛa ì, Binɛa Lefaia ì, Lefaia Ɛlasa ì, Ɛlasa Aseli ì. 
\p  
\v 44 Aseli nɛgↄ̃ɛ ì sooloɛ. An tↄ́n kɛ: Azikaũ, Bokelu, Isimaɛla, Sealia, Obadia ń Ananio. Aseli nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn we píi. 
\c 10  
\s1 Kí Saulu gaa 
\r (1Sam 31.1-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Filitɛ̃ↄ zĩkà ń Isailiↄ, ↄ̃ Isailiↄ bàalɛ̀nɛ́, an daside gàga Giliboa gbɛpↄlɛu.  
\v 2 Kɛ́ Filitɛ̃ↄ pɛ̀lɛ Saulu ń a nɛgↄ̃ɛↄzi, ↄ̃ aa aà nɛ́ↄ Yonatãa ń Abinadabuo ń Malakisuao dɛ̀dɛ.  
\v 3 Zĩ pↄ́ lìaa Sauluzi pãsĩkũ̀, ↄ̃ kàzunaↄ aà pà, à kɛ̀'ĩa.  
\v 4 Ɔ̃ a ò a zĩkabↄkũnaɛ: Ǹ ń fɛ̃nda wo, ní ma zↄ̃ ǹ ma dɛò. Tó ni kɛ màao, gyafↄↄdeɛ beeↄ mↄ kↄ̃̀ↄ'omanↄɛ. Ɔ̃ vĩa aà zĩkabↄkũnapi kũ̀, i weio, ↄ̃ Saulu a fɛ̃nda sɛ̀ à azĩa ò'oa.  
\v 5 Kɛ́ aà zĩkabↄkũnapi è à gà, ↄ̃ à azĩa ò'o a fɛ̃ndaa sↄ̃, aa gà ḿpii.  
\v 6 Màa Saulu ń a nɛgↄ̃ɛ gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃ↄ ń a bɛdeↄ gàga ḿpii sãnu. 
\p  
\v 7 Kɛ́ Isaili pↄ́ kú guzulɛu weↄ è ń zĩgↄ̃ↄ bàalɛ̀ mɛ́ Saulu ń a nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ gàga, ↄ̃ aa bàalɛ̀ sↄ̃, aa ń wɛ̃́lɛↄ tò we, ↄ̃ Filitɛ̃ↄ mↄ̀ zↄ̃̀lɛu.  
\v 8 Kɛ́ a gu dↄ̀, ↄ̃ Filitɛ̃ↄ mↄ̀ pↄ́ↄ woloi gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ gàgaↄwa, ↄ̃ aa Saulu ń a nɛgↄ̃ɛ gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃ↄ gɛ è kálɛa Giliboa gbɛpↄlɛu.  
\v 9 Ɔ̃ aa Saulu mi zↄ̃̀ aa aà gↄ̃kɛbↄↄ wòlowà, ↄ̃ aa gbɛ̃́ↄ zĩ̀ aa a bao fã̀ɛ Filitɛ̃ↄ bùsuu píi ń ń tã́akpɛↄ.  
\v 10 Wà aà gↄ̃kɛbↄↄ kàlɛ ń tã́aↄ kpɛ́u, ↄ̃ wà aà mi lòo Dagↄ̃ kpɛ́u. 
\p  
\v 11 Kɛ́ Yabɛsi Galadadeↄ yã́ pↄ́ Filitɛ̃ↄ kɛ̀ Sauluɛpi mà màa,  
\v 12 ↄ̃ an nɛgↄ̃naↄ fɛ̀lɛ píi, aa Saulu ń a nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ gɛↄ sɛ̀lɛ tàò Yabɛsi. Aa ń vĩ́ gbɛ̃́nɛli gbáu we, ↄ̃ aa lɛyè e gↄↄ sopla. 
\p  
\v 13 Saulu gà kɛ́ à bↄ̀ Dii kpɛ yã́iɛ. I Dii yãdao,\f + \fr 10.13 \ft Lev 19.31, 20.6\f* à gɛ̀ yãgbɛ̀a gɛ̀sisinawa se.\f + \fr 10.13 \ft 1Sam 28.7-8\f* 
\v 14 I yãgbɛa Diiwao. A yã́i Dii aà dɛ̀i, ↄ̃ à Yɛse nɛ́ Davidi kpà kpalau aà gbɛu. 
\c 11  
\s1 Davidi kpaa Isailiↄ kpalau 
\r (2Sam 5.1-10) 
\p  
\v 1 Isailiↄ mↄ̀ Davidi kĩ́i ḿpii Hɛblↄ̃ aa mɛ̀: Wá au doũɛ.  
\v 2 Za zi, baa gↄↄ pↄ́ Saulu dɛ kía ũ, ḿmɛ ni dↄaawɛ̃ɛ zĩlau gɛa ń suao. Ɔ̃ Dii n Lua ònɛ ḿmɛ ńyↄ̃ↄ dɛ a gbɛ̃́ Isailiↄ dↄaana ũ, an kía ũ.  
\v 3 Kɛ́ Isaili gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ mↄ̀ kí Davidi kĩ́i Hɛblↄ̃ ḿpii, we à lɛdoũkɛ̀uńnↄ Dii aɛ, ↄ̃ aa nísikà aà miwa aa aà kpà Isailiↄ kpalau, lá Dii dà Samuɛliɛ a òwa. 
\p  
\v 4 Davidi ń Isailiↄ tↄ̃̀u Yelusalɛũ pↄ́ wì mɛ lↄ Yebusi\f + \fr 11.4 \ft Dↄa 1.21\f* ḿpii. Ɔ̃ Yebusideↄ  
\v 5 ò Davidiɛ: Ńyↄ̃ gɛ̃ lao. Ń beeo Davidi wɛ̃́lɛ bĩ́ide pↄ́ wì mɛ lↄ Siↄnapi sì, ↄ̃ à gↄ̃̀ aà wɛ̃́lɛ ũ.  
\v 6 Gↄↄ bee Davidi mɛ̀: Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dↄ̀aa lɛ̀lɛ Yebusideↄwa káau mɛ́ a gↄ̃ zĩgↄ̃ↄ swana ũ, an gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. Zeluia nɛ́ Yoabu mɛ́ gɛ̀ káau, ↄ̃ à gↄ̃̀ ń swana ũ.  
\v 7 Davidi bɛkpà wɛ̃́lɛ bĩ́idepiu, ↄ̃ wà tↄkpàɛ̀ Davidi Wɛ̃́lɛ.  
\v 8 À kpɛ́ↄ dↄ̀dↄ lìai za gu pↄ́ wà Milo ɛ kàka ń bùsuo e a bĩ́iwa, mɛ́ Yoabu wɛ̃́lɛpi gu pↄ́ gↄ̃̀ↄ kɛ̀kɛ.  
\v 9 Davidi gbãa lɛ́ dɛdɛɛ, asa Dii Zĩgↄ̃de kuaànↄɛ. 
\s1 Davidi nɛgↄ̃naↄ 
\r (2Sam 23.8-39) 
\p  
\v 10 Davidi nɛgↄ̃naↄ kíaↄ yã́n kɛ. Ampiↄ ń Isailiↄ píi aa zɛ̀aànↄ aà kíakɛ yã́ musu. Aa aà kpà Isailiↄ kía ũ lá Dii òwa.  
\v 11 Davidi nɛgↄ̃napiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Akemↄ gbɛ̃́ Yasↄbaũ mɛ́ nɛgↄ̃n tↄde gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃ↄ swana ũ. Aàpi mɛ́ sↄ̃na sɛ̀ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń basↄoↄzi, à ń zↄ̃zↄ̃ò píi gↄↄdoũzĩ. 
\p  
\v 12 Aà gbɛa Dodai nɛ́ Ɛleazaa, Ahoa gbɛ̃́ kú nɛgↄ̃n gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃piↄ guu lↄ.  
\v 13 A kú ń Davidio gↄↄ pↄ́ Filitɛ̃ↄ kã̀aa aa zĩkà Pasadamiũ. Isailiↄ pↄ̀ↄbↄzãkɛ̀ gu pↄ́ naa bú kúu.  
\v 14 Aàpi ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ aamɛ zɛ̀ wà gì búpi guoguo. Aa Filitɛ̃ↄ dɛ̀dɛ, ↄ̃ Dii tò aa zĩ̀ zↄ̃ↄ blè gↄↄ bee. 
\p  
\v 15 Nɛgↄ̃n gbɛ̃ↄn baakwiↄ guu, gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃ↄ mɛ́ bↄ̀ gɛ̀ Davidi kĩ́i Adulaũ gbɛ̀'ɛu. Filitɛ̃ↄ gãli bòo kálɛa Lefai guzulɛu.  
\v 16 Gↄↄ bee Davidi ku sɛ̃gbãu mɛ́ Filitɛ̃ gudↄ̃anaↄ ku Bɛtɛlɛũ.  
\v 17 Davidi lɛ́ a bɛ í nidɛ à mɛ̀: Démɛ a gɛ́ Bɛtɛlɛũ bↄlɛ lↄ̀ↄ'i tↄ́imɛɛi?  
\v 18 Ɔ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃piↄ gɛ̀ gɛ̃̀ Filitɛ̃ↄ bòou, aa Bɛtɛlɛũ bↄlɛ lↄ̀ↄpi í tↄ̀ sùò Davidiɛ. Ɔ̃ i we mìo, a tↄ̃̀lɛ Diiɛ sa'o'i ũɛ.  
\v 19 À mɛ̀: Kai ma Lua, má fↄ̃ íɛ bee mio. Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa gì ń wɛ̃niiↄ auɛ! I we mìo. Nɛgↄ̃n gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃piↄ yãkɛan we. 
\p  
\v 20 Yoabu dãuna Abisai mɛ́ nɛgↄ̃n gbɛ̃ↄn baakwipiↄ swana ũ. Aàpi mɛ́ sↄ̃na sɛ̀ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń basↄoozi à ń dɛdɛ, ↄ̃ à tↄbↄ̀ gbɛ̃ↄn baakwipiↄ guu.  
\v 21 À tↄbↄ̀ dɛ nɛgↄ̃n gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃piↄla, ↄ̃ à gↄ̃̀ ń dↄaana ũ, kási a ku nɛgↄ̃n tↄde gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃piↄ guuo. 
\p  
\v 22 Yoiada nɛ́ Benaia, Kabazee gbɛ̃́á zĩ̀kan wↄ́ↄdeɛ. Aà yãkɛaↄ dasi. À Mↄabu nɛgↄ̃n tↄdeↄ dɛ̀ gbɛ̃ↄn pla. À gɛ̃̀ ɛ guu gↄↄ pↄ́ lougbɛ kwɛ̀, à nↄ̀ↄmusu dɛ̀u.  
\v 23 À Egipi gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ a gbã̀a kà gã̀sĩsuu sↄo dɛ̀. Egipi gbɛ̃́pi sↄ̃mpa dɛ lán zwã̀atãn àsaliwaɛ, ↄ̃ Benaia sↄ̃̀aàzi ń goo, à aà sↄ̃napi sìwà à aà dɛ̀ò.  
\v 24 Yoiada nɛ́ Benaia mɛ́ yã́piↄ kɛ̀, ↄ̃ à tↄbↄ̀ nɛgↄ̃n gbɛ̃ↄn baakwipiↄ guu.  
\v 25 À tↄbↄ̀ dɛ nɛgↄ̃n gbɛ̃ↄn baakwipiↄla, kási a ku nɛgↄ̃n tↄde gbɛ̃ↄn àaↄ̃piↄ guuo. Ɔ̃ Davidi aà dìlɛ a dↄaiↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. 
\p  
\v 26 Nɛgↄ̃napiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: 
\q1 Yoabu dãuna Asaɛli, 
\q1 Dodo nɛ́ Ɛlana Bɛtɛlɛũ gbɛ̃́, 
\q1  
\v 27 Alodi gbɛ̃́ Samↄ, 
\q1 Peloni gbɛ̃́ Ɛlɛzi, 
\q1  
\v 28 Tekoa gbɛ̃́ Ikesi nɛ́ Ila, 
\q1 Anato gbɛ̃́ Abiɛzɛɛ, 
\q1  
\v 29 Usa gbɛ̃́ Sibekai, 
\q1 Ahoa gbɛ̃́ Ilai, 
\q1  
\v 30 Nɛtofa gbɛ̃́ Malai, 
\q1 Nɛtofa gbɛ̃́ Baana nɛ́ Ɛlɛbu, 
\q1  
\v 31 Gibɛa pↄ́ kú Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ bùsuu gbɛ̃́ Libai nɛ́ Itai, 
\q1 Pilatↄ̃ gbɛ̃́ Benaia, 
\q1  
\v 32 Gaasi guzulɛ gbɛ̃́ Idai, 
\q1 Alaba gbɛ̃́ Abiɛli, 
\q1  
\v 33 Bauliũ gbɛ̃́ Azemavɛ, 
\q1 Saaleboni gbɛ̃́ Ɛliaba, 
\q1  
\v 34 Gizoni gbɛ̃́ Asɛũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ, 
\q1 gusĩsĩde gbɛ̃́ Sage nɛ́ Yonatãa, 
\q1  
\v 35 gusĩsĩde gbɛ̃́ Sakaa nɛ́ Ahiaũ, 
\q1 Ulu nɛ́ Ɛlifala, 
\q1  
\v 36 Mɛkɛla gbɛ̃́ Efɛɛ, 
\q1 Peloni gbɛ̃́ Ahia, 
\q1  
\v 37 Kaamɛli gbɛ̃́ Ɛzɛlo, 
\q1 Ɛzɛbai nɛ́ Naalai, 
\q1  
\v 38 Natã dãuna Yoɛli, 
\q1 Ageli nɛ́ Mibaa, 
\q1  
\v 39 Amↄni bui Zɛlɛki, 
\q1 Beelo gbɛ̃́ Naalai, Zeluia nɛ́ Yoabu zĩkabↄkũna, 
\q1  
\v 40 Yɛtɛɛ buiↄ Ila ń Galebuo 
\q1  
\v 41 Iti bui Uli, 
\q1 Alai nɛ́ Zabada, 
\q1  
\v 42 Siza nɛ́ Adina, Lubɛni buiↄ swana 
\q1 ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn baakwi. 
\q1  
\v 43 Maaka nɛ́ Anana, 
\q1 Miti gbɛ̃́ Yosafa, 
\q1  
\v 44 Asalo gbɛ̃́ Uzia, 
\q1 Aloee gbɛ̃́ Otaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ Sãma ń Yeiɛlio, 
\q1  
\v 45 Simɛli nɛ́ Yediaɛ 
\q1 ń a dãuna Yoha Tizi gbɛ̃́o, 
\q1  
\v 46 Maava gbɛ̃́ Ɛliɛli, 
\q1 Ɛlinaaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ Yelibai ń Yosaviao, 
\q1 Mↄabu gbɛ̃́ Itamaa, 
\q1  
\v 47 Ɛliɛli ń Ɔbɛdio 
\q1 ń Mɛzobi gbɛ̃́ Yaasiɛo. 
\c 12  
\s1 Zĩgↄ̃ pↄ́ nà Davidiwa Saulu gↄↄↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Kɛ́ Kisi nɛ́ Saulu Davidi yà, gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa nà Davidiwa Zikilagaↄ tↄ́n kɛ. Aa ku nɛgↄ̃na pↄ́ dↄ̀aàlɛ zĩlauↄ guuɛ.  
\v 2 Aa sáↄ ń gbɛmaↄ kũa, aaì ka ge gbɛ zu ń ↄplaao ń ↄzɛɛo píiɛ. Saulu zĩa bui Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄnɛ, aan kɛ: 
\p  
\v 3 An swana Ahiɛzɛɛ, Gibɛa gbɛ̃́ Semaanɛ ń aà dãuna Yoasio, Azemavɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ Yeziɛli ń Pɛlɛtio, Belaka ń Anato gbɛ̃́ Yehuo,  
\v 4 Gabaↄ̃ↄ gbɛ̃́ Isimaia pↄ́ dɛ nɛgↄ̃n gbɛ̃ↄn baakwiↄ dↄaanaↄ do ũ,  
\v 5 Selemia, Yaaziɛ, Yohanani, Gedela gbɛ̃́ Yozaba,  
\v 6 Ɛluzai, Yelimↄ, Bealia, Semalia, Alufi bui Sefatia,  
\v 7 Ɛlikana, Isia, Azalɛli, Kole buiↄ Yoɛzɛɛ ń Yasↄbaũo  
\v 8 ń Gedoo gbɛ̃́ Yeloaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ Yoela ń Zebadiao. 
\p  
\v 9 Gada buieↄ ńzĩa kpà Davidiwa sɛ̃gbãu. Gↄ̃sa gbãaↄnɛ. Aaìↄ ku zĩ̀ sↄu guuɛ, mɛ́ aa sɛ̀ngbao ń sↄ̃nao dↄ̃. An oa bↄ̀ nↄ̀ↄmusuwa, mɛ́ aaìↄ wãa gusĩsĩdeu lán tuewa.  
\v 10 Ezɛɛ mɛ́ ń swana ũ, a plaade Obadia, a àaↄ̃de Ɛliabu,  
\v 11 a síiↄ̃de Misimana, a sↄode Zelemii,  
\v 12 a soolode Atai, a soplade Ɛliɛli,  
\v 13 a swaaↄ̃de Yohanani, a kɛ̃okwide Ɛlizaba,  
\v 14 a kwide Zelemii, a kuɛdode Mabanai. 
\p  
\v 15 Gada buipiↄá zĩgↄ̃ swanaↄnɛ. An gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ a gbãa kɛ̃́sãańzi gbãa mɛ́ sáa ń gbɛ̃ↄn basↄoↄ gbãao. An gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dɛńlaↄ sↄ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa sↄo pↄ́.  
\v 16 Ɔ̃mɛ bùa Yuudɛ̃wa mↄ sɛ̃́ia guu gↄↄ pↄ́ à pà, aa tò guzulɛdeↄ tilɛ̀ gukpɛ ń bɛ'aɛo píi. 
\p  
\v 17 Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buieↄ ń Yudaeↄ mↄ̀ nà Davidiwa sɛ̃gbãu lↄ.  
\v 18 Davidi gɛ̀ dàńlɛ à mɛ̀: Tó aafia álɛ mↄa à dↄmalɛ, mí gbãakpaázi ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo. Tó álɛ mↄ́ ma kpái ma ibɛɛↄwa, baa kɛ́ mi yãpãsĩkɛɛ́oɛ sↄ̃, wá deziↄ Lua a e, i yã́gↄ̃gↄ̃wɛ̃ɛ.  
\v 19 Ɔ̃ Lua Nisĩna dɛ̀dɛ nɛgↄ̃n gbɛ̃ↄn baakwipiↄ swana Amasaiwa à mɛ̀: 
\q1 N gbɛ̃́ↄn wá ũ, Davidi, 
\q1 wa zɛnnↄɛ, Yɛse nɛ́. 
\q1 Lua aafia kã́fĩnɛ, 
\q1 Lua n dↄnlɛdeↄ gba aafia lↄ, 
\q1 asa n Lua a dↄnlɛɛ. 
\m Ɔ̃ Davidi ń dílɛ à ń kɛ́ a zĩgↄ̃ gbãamↄnɛdeↄ swanaↄ ũ. 
\p  
\v 20 Manase buieↄ nà Davidiwa gↄↄ pↄ́ aàpi ń Filitɛ̃ↄ lɛ́ gɛ́ zĩkai ń Sauluo. Ɔ̃ Davidi ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ i dↄ Filitɛ̃ↄlɛo, asa Filitɛ̃ kíaↄ mɛ́ lɛkpàaĩ, ↄ̃ aa aà gbàɛ aa mɛ̀: Tó à zɛ̀ ń a dii Sauluoɛ, aa wá mi zↄ̃zↄ̃ɛ.  
\v 21 Manase bui pↄ́ nà Davidiwa gↄↄ pↄ́ à tà Zikilagaↄn kɛ: Adena, Yozaba, Yediaɛ, Mikaila, Yozaba, Ɛlihu ń Ziletaio. Aamɛ Manase bui zĩgↄ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄoↄ dↄaanaↄ ũ.  
\v 22 Aa dↄ̀ Davidilɛ gbãamↄnɛdeↄ yã́ musu, asa gↄ̃sa gbãaↄnɛ ḿpii, Davidi zĩgↄ̃ↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄnɛ.  
\v 23 Lá gu lɛ́ dↄ wìↄ mↄ Davidi kĩ́i dↄiaàlɛ e aà zĩgↄ̃ↄ gɛ̀ dasikũ̀ lán Lua ìwaↄwaɛ. 
\s1 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ nà Davidiwa Hɛblↄ̃ↄ 
\p  
\v 24 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa gↄ̃kɛbↄↄ kũa aa mↄ̀ Hɛblↄ̃ Davidi kpái kpalau Saulu gbɛu lá Dii òwaↄ dasilɛn kɛ:  
\v 25 Yuda pↄ́ sɛ̀ngbao ń sↄ̃naↄ kũaↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ soolo n ↄ̀aa síiↄ̃oɛ (6.800).  
\v 26 Simɛↄ buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ sopla ń basↄooɛ (7.100).  
\v 27 Levii buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ síiↄ̃ ń ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃oɛ (4.600).  
\v 28 Aalona buiↄ dↄaana Yoiada ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ àaↄ̃ ń ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń basↄooɛ (3.700).  
\v 29 Ɛ̀waaso nɛgↄ̃n Zadoki kú ń guu ń a bɛ'uabeleↄ gbɛ̃ↄn bao ń plao.  
\v 30 Saulu zĩa bui Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ àaↄ̃ɛ (3.000). Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ bui dasideↄ ku Saulu kpɛ e tiaɛ.  
\v 31 Ɛflaiũ buiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bao ń ↄ̀aa síiↄ̃oɛ (20.800). Gↄ̃sa gbãa tↄdeↄnɛ ń gbɛ̃́ↄ guu.  
\v 32 Manase bui pↄ́ kú bɛ'aɛ oiↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bao plasaiɛ (18.000). Gbɛ̃́piↄ wà ń plɛ́ aa gɛ́ Davidi kpái kpalau.  
\v 33 Isakaa bui dↄaanaↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa doɛ. Aa gↄↄ bee yã́ dↄ̃ mɛ́ aa laai vĩ a yã́ musu, aa dↄ̃ lá à kũ̀ Isailiↄ kɛ. Aa kú ń ń ìwaↄ píi.  
\v 34 Zabulↄni bui pↄ́ aa zĩ dↄ̃ mɛ́ aa gↄ̃kɛbↄ dↄ́ɛ dↄ̃ↄ píi gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ blakwiɛ (50.000). Aa ku aà kpɛ ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndooɛ  
\v 35 Nɛfatali bui dↄaanaↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa sↄoɛ ń ń ìwaↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ baakwi ń soplao (37.000), baade ń a sɛ̀ngbaoo ń a sↄ̃nao.  
\v 36 Dã bui pↄ́ aa ku zĩ̀ sↄu guuↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ baakwi plasaio ń ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃oɛ (28.600).  
\v 37 Asɛɛ bui pↄ́ zĩ dↄ̃ mɛ́ aa ku sↄu guuↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ blaɛ (40.000).  
\v 38 Lubɛni buiↄ ń Gada buiↄ ń Manase bui pↄ́ kú Yuudɛ̃ baaleↄ gbɛ̃ↄn sↄ́sↄo lɛɛ basooloɛ (120.000). An baade ń a gↄ̃kɛbↄↄ. 
\p  
\v 39 Gbɛ̃́piↄá zĩgↄ̃ↄnɛ ḿpii, aaìↄ ku sia zĩlau sↄu guuɛ. Aa mↄ̀ Hɛblↄ̃ ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo Davidi kpái kpalau, i gↄ̃ Isaili bui píi kía ũ. Ɔ̃ Isaili kĩniↄ làasoo doũpi kɛ̀ lↄ, aa ye Davidi kpaa kpalaui.  
\v 40 Ɔ̃ aa gↄↄ àaↄ̃ kɛ̀ ń Davidio we, aa pↄblè aa vɛ̃ɛmì, asa an bɛdeↄ kũ̀sũakɛ̀nɛ́ɛ.  
\v 41 Bee gbɛa an saɛde pↄ́ kú Isakaa buiↄ bùsuu ń Zabulↄni buiↄ bùsuo e à gɛ̀ pɛ̀ Nɛfatali bui pↄ́ kú zã̀ↄ bùsuwaↄ aa pↄblea dì zàa'ĩnaↄnɛ ń yiongoↄ ń sↄ̃baonaↄ ń zuↄ aa mↄ̀onɛ́ɛ. Pↄ́wɛnti diɛ ń kaadↄɛmbɛ giiↄ ń vɛ̃ɛbɛ giiↄ ń vɛ̃ɛo ń nísio ń zuↄ ń sãↄ, kɛ́ Isailiↄ lɛ́ pↄnakɛ yã́i. 
\c 13  
\s1 Sua ń Dii kpagoloo Yelusalɛũ 
\r (2Sam 6.1-11) 
\p  
\v 1 Davidi lɛkpàaĩ ń a zĩgↄ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄoↄ dↄaanaↄ ń a gbɛ̃ↄn basↄobasↄoↄ dↄaanaↄ píi.  
\v 2 Ɔ̃ a ò Isailiↄnɛ píi: Tó à kɛ̀ɛ́ maa, mɛ́ a dɛ Dii wá Lua pↄeã ũɛ, wà lɛ́kpãsãkɛ wá gbɛ̃́ kĩni pↄ́ kú Isaili bùsuuↄnɛ píi ń sa'onaↄ ń Levii bui pↄ́ kúńnↄ ń wɛ̃́lɛↄ guuↄ, aa mↄ kãaawanↄ,  
\v 3 wí gɛ wá Lua kpagolo sɛ́ suò wá kĩ́i, asa wi yãgbɛawà Saulu gↄↄo.  
\v 4 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kãaaapiↄ wèi màa, asa à kɛ̀ ḿpiiɛ maaɛ. 
\p  
\v 5 Ɔ̃ Davidi Isailiↄ kã̀aa za Egipi swa Sikooi e à gɛ̀ pɛ̀ Amata bↄlɛwa, kɛ́ aa Lua kpagolo sɛ́ Kiliayaaliũ aa suò.  
\v 6 Ɔ̃ Davidi ń Isailiↄ gɛ̀ Kiliayaaliũ pↄ́ wì mɛ lↄ Baala, Yuda bùsuu ḿpii, kɛ́ aa gɛ wà Dii Lua kpagolo sɛ́ wà suò. Dii ìↄ kible kpagolopi musu malaika gã̀sĩadeↄ zãnguo\f + \fr 13.6 \ft 1Sam 4.4, Soũ 99.1\f* ↄ̃ aà tↄ́ kuwà.  
\v 7 Ɔ̃ aa kpagolopi sɛ̀ Abinadabu bɛ,\f + \fr 13.7 \ft 1Sam 7.1-2\f* aa dà zugo dafu guu aa dàò zɛ́u, Uza ń Ahio mɛ́ lɛ́ gɛò.  
\v 8 Davidi ń Isailiↄ lɛ́ ↄ̃wã Lua aɛ ń gbãa pua lɛ́u ḿpii ń lɛsiao. Wàlɛ mↄↄnalɛ ń kúuo ń gã̀ao ń sɛ̃́sɛ̃naↄ ń kã̀aeↄ. 
\p  
\v 9 Kɛ́ aa kà Kidↄ̃ ésegbɛ̃kĩi, zuↄ gɛ̃nalɛ̀, ↄ̃ Uza ↄbↄ̀ kpagolopi kũ̀.  
\v 10 Ɔ̃ Dii pↄ pàaàzi à aà lɛ̀ we, kɛ́ à ↄnà kpagolopiwa yã́i, ↄ̃ à gà\f + \fr 13.10 \ft Nao 4.15\f* Lua aɛ we.  
\v 11 Davidi pↄ pà, kɛ́ Dii pↄ fɛ̃̀ Uzazi yã́i, ↄ̃ wì mɛ gupiɛ Pↄfɛ̃a'uzazi e ń a gbão.  
\v 12 Gↄↄ bee ↄ̃ vĩa Davidi kũ̀ Lua yã́ musu à mɛ̀: Kpelewa má kɛ mà Lua kpagolo sɛ́ mà taòi?  
\v 13 Ɔ̃ i sɛ sùò a wɛ̃́lɛu lↄo, à lìlɛ tàò Gata gbɛ̃́ Ɔbɛdɛdↄũ bɛ. 
\p  
\v 14 Lua kpagolopi ku aà bɛ e mↄ àaↄ̃, ↄ̃ Dii ɛ̀fãaikɛ̀ aà bɛdeↄnɛ ń pↄ́ pↄ́ a vĩↄ píi.\f + \fr 13.14 \ft 1Lad 26.4-5\f* 
\c 14  
\s1 Davidi zĩblea Filitɛ̃ↄwa 
\r (2Sam 5.11-25) 
\p  
\v 1 Tii kí Hilaũ gbɛ̃́ↄ zĩ̀ Davidiwa ń sɛdɛ líↄ ń gbɛ̀'ãnaↄ ń li'ãnaↄ kpɛdↄiɛ̀.  
\v 2 Ɔ̃ Davidi dↄ̃̀ sa kɛ́ Dii a kpa Isailiↄ kía ũɛ, mɛ́ à a kpala kã̀fĩɛ maamaa, kɛ́ Isailiↄ dɛ Luapi gbɛ̃́ↄ ũ yã́i. 
\p  
\v 3 Davidi ɛ̀a nↄeↄ sɛ̀ Yelusalɛũ lↄ, ↄ̃ à nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ń nɛnↄɛↄ ì'ińnↄ.  
\v 4 Nɛgↄ̃ɛ pↄ́ à ń í Yelusalɛũpiↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Samua, Sobabu, Natã, Salomↄↄ,  
\v 5 Ibaa, Ɛlisua, Ɛlifele,  
\v 6 Nↄga, Nɛfɛgi, Yafia,  
\v 7 Ɛlisama, Ɛliada ń Ɛlifeleo. 
\p  
\v 8 Kɛ́ Filitɛ̃ↄ mà wà Davidi kpà Isaili bui píi kía ũ, ↄ̃ ampii aa gɛ̀ lɛ́ aà wɛ. Kɛ́ Davidi a baomà, ↄ̃ à gɛ̀ daińlɛ.  
\v 9 Filitɛ̃ↄ mↄ̀ lɛ̀lɛ Lefai guzulɛdeↄwa,  
\v 10 ↄ̃ Davidi gbɛ̀a Luawa à mɛ̀: Mà gɛ́ lɛ́lɛi Filitɛ̃ↄwa, ńyↄ̃ ń namɛɛ ma ↄzĩa? Dii wèwà à mɛ̀: Gɛ́, má ń nanɛ n ↄzĩ.  
\v 11 Ɔ̃ Davidi ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ gɛ̀ Baali Pelaziũ, ↄ̃ à zĩblèmá we. Davidi mɛ̀: Lua dↄ̀aamɛɛ à bↄ̀ mↄ̀ ma ibɛɛↄwa ń gbãao, lá í ì gufↄ̃ bùiwa. Ɔ̃ à tↄkpà gupiɛ Baali Pelaziũ.\f + \fr 14.11 \ft Bee mɛ̀ Dii bↄ̀ bùi.\f* 
\v 12 Filitɛ̃ↄ ń tã́aↄ tò we, ↄ̃ Davidi mɛ̀ wà kpasa. 
\p  
\v 13 Ɔ̃ Filitɛ̃ↄ ɛ̀a mↄ̀ lɛ̀lɛ Lefai guzulɛdeↄwa lↄ.  
\v 14 Ɔ̃ Davidi ɛ̀a gbɛ̀a Luawa lↄ. Lua wèwà à mɛ̀: Ńsu gɛ́má súsuo. Liańzi, ní lɛ́lɛmá bↄaa ń kpɛ̃̀ kpɛ́o.  
\v 15 Tó a táa'okĩi mà lípiↄ mia, à bↄmá ń zĩo, asa ma bↄ dↄaaɛ́n we, kɛ́ mà zĩble Filitɛ̃ zĩgↄ̃ↄwa yã́i.  
\v 16 Davidi kɛ̀ màa lá Lua òɛwa, ↄ̃ aa zĩblè Filitɛ̃ zĩgↄ̃ↄwa za Gabaↄ̃ↄ e à gɛ̀ pɛ̀ Gɛzɛɛwa.  
\v 17 Davidi tↄ́ lì bùsuↄla píi, ↄ̃ Dii tò bui píi vĩakɛ̀ɛ̀. 
\c 15  
\s1 Sua ń Dii kpagoloo Yelusalɛũ 
\r (2Sam 6.12-22) 
\p  
\v 1 Kɛ́ Davidi kpɛdↄ̀dↄ azĩaɛ a wɛ̃́lɛ guu, ↄ̃ à gukɛ̀kɛ Lua kpagoloɛ, à zwã̀akpɛ dↄ̀ɛ̀  
\v 2 à mɛ̀: Gbɛ̃e Lua kpagolo sɛa zɛ́ vĩo, sema Levii buiↄ bàasio, asa Dii mɛ́ ń dílɛ a sɛnaↄ ũ, aaiↄ a zĩ kɛ gↄↄpii. 
\p  
\v 3 À Isaili bui píi kã̀aa Yelusalɛũ, kɛ́ aa gɛ Dii kpagolopi sɛ suò gu pↄ́ a kɛ̀kɛɛ̀u.  
\v 4 Ɔ̃ à Aalona buiↄ ń Levii buiↄ sìsi:  
\v 5 Kɛata buiↄ dↄaana Uliɛli ń a gbɛ̃́ gbɛ̃ↄn basooloↄ.  
\v 6 Mɛlali buiↄ dↄaana Asaia ń a gbɛ̃́ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń baooↄ.  
\v 7 Geesↄ̃ buiↄ dↄaana Yoɛli ń a gbɛ̃́ gbɛ̃ↄn basoolokwiↄ.  
\v 8 Ɛlizafã buiↄ dↄaana Semaia ń a gbɛ̃́ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa doↄ.  
\v 9 Hɛblↄ̃ buiↄ dↄaana Ɛliɛli ń a gbɛ̃́ gbɛ̃ↄn basiiↄ̃ↄ.  
\v 10 Uziɛli buiↄ dↄaana Aminadabu ń a gbɛ̃́ gbɛ̃ↄn basↄokwi ń plaoↄ. 
\p  
\v 11 Ɔ̃ Davidi sa'onkiaↄ Zadoki ń Abiataao sìsi ń Levii buiↄ Uliɛli, Asaia, Yoɛli, Semaia, Ɛliɛli ń Aminadabuo.  
\v 12 A ònɛ́: Levii bui dↄaanaↄn á ũ. Ápiↄ ń á gbɛ̃́ↄ à gbãbↄ ázĩaɛ, í gɛ́ Dii Isailiↄ Lua kpagolo sɛ́ à suò gu pↄ́ má kɛ̀kɛɛ̀u.  
\v 13 Dii wá Lua pↄ fɛ̃̀wázi káau, kɛ́ á Levii buiↄ ámɛ á sɛao yã́i. Wi yãgbɛawà a zɛ́wao.  
\v 14 Ɔ̃ Sa'onaↄ ń Levii bui kĩniↄ gbãbↄ̀ ńzĩaɛ, kɛ́ aa Dii Isailiↄ Lua kpagolo sɛ suò yã́i.  
\v 15 Ɔ̃ Levii buipiↄ gɛ̀ Lua kpagolo sɛ dà ń gã̀u, aalɛ suò ń a sɛ́liↄ lá Dii ò Mↄiziɛwa. 
\p  
\v 16 Ɔ̃ Davidi ò Levii bui dↄaanaↄnɛ aa ń gbɛ̃eↄ dilɛ aaↄ lɛsi ń pↄ́'ↄbↄnaↄ: Domaↄ ń mↄↄnaↄ ń sɛ̃́sɛ̃naↄ, an pↄna súu iↄ dↄ.  
\v 17 Ɔ̃ Levii buipiↄ Yoɛli nɛ́ Emani dìlɛ ń Bɛlɛkia nɛ́ Asafao ń Mɛlali bui Kusaia nɛ́ Etanio.  
\v 18 An kwàasiↄn kɛ: Zakali, Yaaziɛ, Semilamↄ, Yeiɛli, Uni, Ɛliabu, Benaia, Maasea, Matitia, Ɛlifeleu, Mikinɛia, Ɔbɛdɛdↄũ, Yeiɛli ń Azaziao.  
\v 19 Lɛ̀sin dↄaanaↄ Emani, Asafa ń Etanio lɛ́ mↄgotɛ̃ sɛ̃́sɛ̃naↄ lɛ́.  
\v 20 Zakali, Aziɛli, Semilamↄ, Yeiɛli, Uni, Ɛliabu, Maasea ń Benaiao lɛ́ doma'ↄ gèele lɛ́.  
\v 21 Matitia, Ɛlifeleu, Mikinɛia, Ɔbɛdɛdↄũ, Yeiɛli ń Azaziao lɛ́ mↄↄna'ↄ kelena lɛ́. 
\p  
\v 22 Levii bui dↄaana Kenania mɛ́ kpagolosɛnaↄ dↄaana ũ. Ì yãdanɛ́, kɛ́ a dↄ̃a vĩ a guu yã́i.  
\v 23 Bɛlɛkia ń Ɛlikanao mɛ́ kpagolopi dↄ̃̀anaↄ ũ.  
\v 24 Sa'onaɛ beeↄ mɛ́ lɛ́ kã̀aepɛ Lua kpagolo aɛ: Sebania, Yosafa, Nɛtanɛli, Amasai, Zakali, Benaia ń Ɛliɛzɛɛo. Ɔbɛdɛdↄũ ń Yehiao dɛ a dↄ̃̀anaↄ ũɛ lↄ. 
\p  
\v 25 Màa Davidi ń Isailiↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ ń zĩgↄ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄoↄ dↄaanaↄ gɛ̀ Dii bàakuańnↄ kpagolo sɛ̀ Ɔbɛdɛdↄũ bɛ, aalɛ suò ń pↄnao.  
\v 26 Lua dↄ̀ Levii bui pↄ́ kpagolopi sɛaↄlɛ, ↄ̃ wà sa'ò ń zuswanaↄ mɛ̀n sopla ń sãsakaoↄ mɛ̀n sopla lↄ.  
\v 27 Davidi bàabaa gomusu daa ń Levii bui pↄ́ kpagolo sɛaↄ ń ń dↄaana Kenaniao ń lɛ̀sinaↄ píi. Davidi bàabaa sa'o'ula daa lↄ.  
\v 28 Màa Isaili bui píi lɛ́ su ń Dii kpagoloo ń kúkuakɛao ń kuu'ↄo ń kã̀ae'ↄo ń sɛ̃́sɛ̃n ↄ́o ń domalɛao ń mↄↄnlɛao. 
\p  
\v 29 Kɛ́ Dii kpagolo lɛ́ gɛ̃ Davidi wɛ̃́lɛu, Saulu nɛ́ Mikali lɛ́ zĩ́lɛ gwa fɛnɛntiu. Kɛ́ a è kí Davidi lɛ́ ↄ̃wã, àlɛ pↄnakɛ Dii aɛ, ↄ̃ à sakàaàgu a sↄ̃ guu. 
\c 16  
\p  
\v 1 Wà sù ń Lua kpagoloo wa dìlɛ zwã̀akpɛ pↄ́ Davidi dↄ̀ɛ̀ guu. Ɔ̃ wà sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ ò Lua aɛ ń sáaukpasaↄ.  
\v 2 Kɛ́ Davidi sa'ò a làa, à báaadà gbɛ̃́ↄgu ń Dii tↄ́o.  
\v 3 Ɔ̃ à pɛ̃ɛ ń damina kàao ń vɛ̃ɛbɛ kàao bìilɛ Isaili pↄ́ kãaaa weↄnɛ ń miwa mɛ̀ndodo gↄ̃ɛↄ ń nↄɛↄ. 
\p  
\v 4 À Levii buieↄ dìlɛ aaↄ zĩkɛ Dii kpagolo aɛ, aaiↄ Dii Isailiↄ Lua tↄbↄ, aaiↄ aà sáaukpa, aaiↄ aà táasilɛ.  
\v 5 Asafa mɛ́ ń gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ, Zakali mɛ́ aà plaade ũ, bee gbɛa Yaaziɛ, Semilamↄ, Yeiɛli, Matitia, Ɛliabu, Benaia, Ɔbɛdɛdↄũ ń Yeiɛlio. Aaliↄ domaↄ lɛ́ ń mↄↄnaↄ. Asafa sↄ̃ aliↄ sɛ̃́sɛ̃napa.  
\v 6 Sa'onaↄ Benaia ń Yaaziɛo mɛ́ aaliↄ kã̀aepɛ Luabaakuańnↄ kpagolo aɛ gↄↄpii. 
\s1 Lua a gbɛ̃́ↄ suabaa 
\r (Soũ 105.1-15) 
\p  
\v 7 Gↄↄ bee ↄ̃ Davidi Dii sáaukpazĩ dàalɛ, a nà Asafa ń a gbɛ̃́ↄnɛ ń ↄzĩ. 
\q1  
\v 8 À Dii sáaukpa, í aà sísi, 
\q1 à to bui píi aà yãkɛaↄ dↄ̃. 
\q1  
\v 9 À lɛsi à aà táasilɛ, 
\q1 í aà yãbↄnsaɛkɛaↄ galikɛ píi, 
\q1  
\v 10 í ĩ́anadã ń aà tↄ́ pↄ́ a kua adoao. 
\q1 Á Dii kĩ́i wɛ̀ɛlɛnaↄ à pↄnakɛ, 
\q1  
\v 11 à gɛ Dii le à gbãa gbɛawà, 
\q1 íↄ aà aɛya gↄↄpii. 
\q1  
\v 12 À to yãbↄnsaɛ pↄ́ a kɛ̀ↄ dↄágu, 
\q1 aà dabudabukɛaↄ ń yã́ pↄ́ a dìlɛↄ. 
\q1  
\v 13 Á Dii zↄ̀blena Isaili buiↄ, 
\q1 á Yakↄbu bui pↄ́ à á sɛ́piↄ, 
\q1  
\v 14 Dii mɛ́ wá Lua ũ, 
\q1 ↄ̃mɛ ì yãdilɛ gbɛ̃́piiɛ. 
\q1  
\v 15 Aà bàakuawanↄ yã́ lí sãaaguo, 
\q1 yã́ pↄ́ a òpi aↄ ku e wá buiwaɛ. 
\q1  
\v 16 Aà bàa kú ń Ablahaũo,\f + \fr 16.16 \ft Daa 12.7, 17.8\f* 
\q1 à ɛ̀a yã́ doũpi lɛgbɛ̃̀ Izaakiɛ lↄ.\f + \fr 16.16 \ft Daa 26.3\f* 
\q1  
\v 17 Aà bàa ɛ̀a kú ń Yakↄbuo iko ũ, 
\q1 ↄ̃ a kú ń Isailiↄ e gↄↄpii. 
\q1  
\v 18 À mɛ̀ á Kanaa bùsu kpámá, 
\q1 aↄ dɛ pↄ́ pↄ́ aa sɛ kpaalɛ guu ũ.\f + \fr 16.18 \ft Daa 28.13\f* 
\q1  
\v 19 Gↄↄ bee aa dasio, wìli ń yãdao, 
\q1 aa ku Kanaa bùsuu bↄ̀mↄↄ ũɛ. 
\q1  
\v 20 Aaìↄ liaaliaa bui ń buio guuɛ, 
\q1 aaìↄ bɛbɛ bùsu ń bùsuo. 
\q1  
\v 21 I we gbɛ̃e ń wɛtã̀o, 
\q1 à kíaↄ lèle an yã́ musu à mɛ̀: 
\q1  
\v 22 Aasu ↄkã gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ a ń sɛ́piↄwao, 
\q1 aasu ĩada a ãnabipiↄwao.\f + \fr 16.22 \ft Daa 20.3-7\f* 
\s1 Dii mɛ́ kía zↄ̃ↄ ũ 
\r (Soũ 96.1-13, 106.1, 47-48) 
\q1  
\v 23 Dṹnia gbɛ̃́pii, à lɛsi Diiɛ. 
\q1 Àↄ aà zĩblea baokpa lá gu lɛ́ dↄ. 
\q1  
\v 24 À aà gawi yã'o buiↄnɛ, 
\q1 à aà yãbↄnsaɛↄ galikɛ gbɛ̃́piiɛ. 
\q1  
\v 25 Dii zↄ̃ↄ, à kà wà aà táasilɛ, 
\q1 à kà wà vĩakɛɛ̀ dɛ diiↄla píi. 
\q1  
\v 26 Buipãleↄ diiↄá pↄ́ gianaↄnɛ, 
\q1 Dii mɛ́ musu kɛ̀. 
\q1  
\v 27 A zↄ̃ↄkɛ ń bɛɛɛo vĩ, 
\q1 gbãa ń pↄnao ku aà kĩ́iɛ. 
\q1  
\v 28 À gawi ń gbãao dↄ̃ Diiɛ, 
\q1 bùsu píi gbɛ̃́ↄ, à dↄ̃ Diiɛ. 
\q1  
\v 29 À Dii tↄ́ gawi dↄ̃ɛ̀, 
\q1 à mↄ aà aɛ, í aà gba pↄ́, 
\q1 à kúlɛ Diiɛ ń lousisi'ulaↄ daa. 
\q1  
\v 30 Zĩ́lɛdeↄ à tó á mɛ àↄ kukɛ aà aɛ. 
\q1 À dṹnia kàlɛ gíũgiũ, a deea vĩo. 
\q1  
\v 31 Musudeↄ, à pↄnakɛ, 
\q1 zĩ́lɛdeↄ, à vĩ àↄ kɛ̃aa, 
\q1 í o buiↄ guu Dii mɛ́ lɛ́ kible. 
\q1  
\v 32 Ísia ń pↄ́ pↄ́ kúuↄ, à kↄ̃fĩkɛ, 
\q1 sɛ̃̀a ń pↄ́ pↄ́ kúuↄ, à kúkuakɛ píi, 
\q1  
\v 33 lí pↄ́ kú lákpɛuↄ i gulakɛ, 
\q1 aai pↄnakɛ Dii aɛ, 
\q1 asa àlɛ mↄ́ yã́kpalɛkɛi ń dṹniaoɛ. 
\q1  
\v 34 À Dii sáaukpa, asa a maa, 
\q1 aà gbɛ̃kɛ láaa vĩo. 
\q1  
\v 35 À mɛ: Lua wá Suabana, wá suaba! 
\q1 Wá bↄlɛ buiↄ guu, ní wá kãaa, 
\q1 wí n tↄ́ kã́fĩ, asa a kua adoa, 
\q1 wí ĩ́anadã ń n táasilɛao. 
\q1  
\v 36 Wà Dii Isailiↄ Lua sáaukpa 
\q1 za asĩnizĩ e gↄↄpii! 
\m Ɔ̃ gbɛ̃́pii mɛ̀: Ãmi! Àleluya! 
\p  
\v 37 Davidi Asafa ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ dìlɛ Dii bàakuańnↄ kpagoloi, kɛ́ aaliↄ zĩkɛ a aɛ lá gu lɛ́ dↄ lá wa dìlɛwa.  
\v 38 À Ɔbɛdɛdↄũ ń a gbɛ̃́ gbɛ̃ↄn bàaↄ̃kwi plasaiↄ dìlɛ we lↄ. Yedutu nɛ́ Ɔbɛdɛdↄũpi ń Osao mɛ́ bↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ũ.  
\v 39 À sa'onkia Zadoki ń a gbɛ̃ sa'onaↄ dìlɛ Dii zwã̀akpɛ kĩ́i Gabaↄ̃ↄ gulɛsĩ pↄ́ wa bòu,  
\v 40 kɛ́ aaliↄ sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ o Dii gbagbakĩiwa kↄↄ ń oosio, lá a ku Dii ikoyã pↄ́ a dìlɛ Isailiↄnɛ lá guuwa.  
\v 41 Emani ń Yedutuo kúńnↄ we ń gbɛ̃́ kĩni pↄ́ wà ń tↄ́ sì wà ń sɛ́ↄ, kɛ́ aaↄ Dii sáaukpa, asa aà gbɛ̃kɛ láaa vĩo.  
\v 42 Kã̀aeↄ ń sɛ̃́sɛ̃naↄ ń pↄ́'ↄbↄn pãleↄ dɛ Emani ń Yedutupio yã́ ũɛ, kɛ́ wàli lɛsiò Luaɛ. Yedutupi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ mɛ́ bↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ũ.  
\v 43 Kɛ́ baade tà a bɛ, ↄ̃ Davidi ɛ̀a tà à samaa'ò a uadeↄnɛ. 
\c 17  
\s1 Lua lɛgbɛ̃a Davidiɛ 
\r (2Sam 7.1-17) 
\p  
\v 1 Kɛ́ kí zↄ̃̀lɛ a bɛ, a ò ãnabi Natãɛ: Ée! Kpɛ́ pↄ́ wa dↄ̀ ń sɛdɛ lío ↄ̃ máↄ zↄ̃lɛu, Dii bàakuawanↄ kpagolo iↄ dilɛa zwã̀akpɛua?  
\v 2 Natã wèwà à mɛ̀: Lá à n pↄ gbàn kɛ, asa Lua kunnↄɛ.  
\v 3 Gwãasĩna bee Dii yã'ò Natãɛ à mɛ̀:  
\v 4 Gɛ ǹ o ma zↄ̀blena Davidiɛ ma mɛ̀ ↄ̃mɛ a bɛ pↄ́ máↄ ku a guu kpamɛɛo.  
\v 5 Za gↄↄ pↄ́ ma bↄ ń Isailiↄ Egipi e gbã mi bɛkpao. Miↄ sↄ̃kĩikpakpaɛ, zwã̀akpɛ mɛ́ ma zↄ̃lɛkĩi ũ.  
\v 6 Gu pↄ́ ma sↄ̃kĩikpàu ń ma gbɛ̃́ Isailiↄ píi mi dↄaanaↄ dilɛ aa dↄaanɛ́ɛ, kási mi o ń gbɛ̃eɛ, bↄ́yãi i kpɛdↄmɛɛ ń sɛdɛ líoo nio.  
\v 7 Gɛ ǹ o ma zↄ̀blena Davidipiɛ, ma Dii Zĩgↄ̃de ma mɛ̀ ma aà sɛ̀ sãdãdãkĩi, kɛ́ aàↄ dɛ ma gbɛ̃́ Isailiↄ dↄaana ũɛ.  
\v 8 Gu pↄ́ à gɛ̀u píi miↄ kuaànↄɛ, ↄ̃ ma aà ibɛɛↄ dɛ̀dɛɛ̀. Má aà tↄbↄ maamaa saɛ, iↄ dɛ dṹnia tↄdeↄ do ũ.  
\v 9 Ma bùsu kpà ma gbɛ̃́ Isailiↄwa ma ń kálɛu, ↄ̃ aa zↄ̃̀lɛu aa gↄ̃̀ vĩ. Aa sↄ̃̀deedeekɛ lↄo. Gbɛ̃vãiↄ e ń wɛtã lá aa ń wɛtã̀ káau  
\v 10 gↄↄ pↄ́ ma dↄaanaↄ dìlɛnɛ́wa lↄo. Má aà ibɛɛpiↄ busaɛ̀ píiɛ. 
\p Ma Dii málɛ oɛ̀, mámɛ má bɛkpaɛ̀ aà buiↄ gbãa'ekĩi ũ.  
\v 11 Tó aà gↄↄ pà à gà, má aà nɛgↄ̃ɛ mɛ̀ndo sɛ lɛsĩɛ, mí aà kpa kpalau.\f + \fr 17.11 \ft Soũ 89.3-4, 132.11, Zãa 7.42, Zĩn 2.30\f* 
\v 12 Aàpi mɛ́ a kpɛdↄmɛɛ, iↄ ku kpalau e gↄↄpii.  
\v 13 Mámɛ máↄ dɛ aà mae ũ, aàpi iↄ dɛ ma nɛ́ ũ.\f + \fr 17.13 \ft Soũ 2.7, 89.26-27, 2Kln 6.18, Ɛbɛ 1.5\f* Má gbɛ̃kɛ bↄaaaànↄ lá má bↄ̀aa ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú aà ãawao.  
\v 14 Má aà buipi kpa kpala pↄ́ bↄ̀ ma kĩ́iu, iↄ ku we e gↄↄpii, iↄ dɛ ma gbɛ̃́ↄ kía ũ, mɛ́ aà kpalapi aↄ láaa vĩo.\f + \fr 17.14 \ft Soũ 89.36-37\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Ɔ̃ Natã yã́pi dàu a sìu Davidiɛ lá Dii òɛwa píi. 
\s1 Davidi wabikɛa Diiwa 
\r (2Sam 7.18-29) 
\p  
\v 16 Ɔ̃ kí Davidi gɛ̃̀ zↄ̃̀lɛ Dii aɛ à mɛ̀: Dii Lua, bↄ́n ma ũi? Deↄn ma bɛdeↄ ũ ↄ̃ n ma ka gweaɛ taawai?  
\v 17 Lua, bee kɛ̀nɛ fɛ̃́nɛũ e tia, ↄ̃ n mapi n zↄ̀blena bui pↄ́ aↄ ku zia yã'ò lↄ. Dii Lua, ↄ̃ n ma dilɛ lándↄ̃ má dɛ gbɛ̃́piilawaa?  
\v 18 Dii Lua, kpelewa má o sa mapi n zↄ̀blena kã́fĩa yã́ musu lↄi? Ń ma dↄ̃.  
\v 19 Dii, n yãzↄ̃ↄpi kɛ̀ lá ń yeiwa ma yã́iɛ, ↄ̃ ń tò mapi n zↄ̀blena má yãzↄ̃ↄpiↄ dↄ̃ píi.  
\v 20 Dii, gbɛ̃e muaannↄo. Diie kuo, n bàasio, lá wá màwa.  
\v 21 Démɛ muaa ń n gbɛ̃́ Isailiↄi? Dṹnia buiↄ guu bui mɛ̀ndopi ↄ̃ ń bò n gbɛ̃́ↄ ũ. N nzĩa tↄbↄ̀, n yãzↄ̃ↄ bↄnsaɛↄ kɛ̀ n gbɛ̃́piↄnɛ, n buieↄ yà n gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ n ń bó Egipiↄnɛ.  
\v 22 N Isailiↄ dìlɛ aaↄ dɛ n gbɛ̃́ↄ ũ e gↄↄpiiɛ. Dii, n gↄ̃ ń Lua ũ.  
\v 23 Dii, to lɛ́ pↄ́ ń gbɛ̃̀ mapi n zↄ̀blena ń ma buiↄ yã́ musu àↄ ku gↄↄpii. Kɛ lá ń òwa,  
\v 24 ní tↄbↄ maamaa e gↄↄpii, wi mɛ Dii Zĩgↄ̃deá Isailiↄ Luaɛ, mɛ́ mapi n zↄ̀blena Davidi, ńyↄ̃ ma buiↄ zĩ́napɛlɛ,  
\v 25 asa mpi ma Lua, ń òmɛɛ n mɛ̀ ńyↄ̃ bɛkpamɛɛ ma buiↄ gbãa'ekĩi ũɛ. A yã́i tò mapi n zↄ̀blena ma sↄ̃dìlɛ ma wabiɛ bee kɛ̀ma.  
\v 26 Dii, ḿmɛnn Lua, ↄ̃ n yãmaapi ò mapi n zↄ̀blenaɛ.  
\v 27 Báaada mapi n zↄ̀blena ma buiↄgu sa, níↄ wɛ́tɛńzi gↄↄpii. Dii, ḿmɛ n báaadàńgu, aaↄ báaa vĩ e gↄↄpiiɛ. 
\c 18  
\s1 Davidi zĩblea buipãleↄwa 
\r (2Sam 8.1-18) 
\p  
\v 1 Bee gbɛa Davidi zĩblè Filitɛ̃ↄwa, à ń busa à Gata ń a wɛ̃́lɛↄ sìmá.  
\v 2 À zĩblè Mↄabuↄwa, ↄ̃ aa gↄ̃̀ aà zↄ̀blenaↄ ũ, aaiↄ falubↄɛ̀.  
\v 3 Davidi zĩblè Zoba kí Adadɛzɛɛwa Amata gↄↄ pↄ́ à ɛ̀a lɛ́ gɛ́ ↄtↄ̃i Uflata swasaɛdeↄwa.  
\v 4 À aà sↄ̃́goↄ kũ̀kũ mɛ̀n ↄ̀aa sↄo (1.000) ń sↄ̃́godeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ sopla (7.000) ń kɛ̀sɛdeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bao (20.000). À ń sↄ̃́ↄ kĩzã zↄ̃̀zↄ̃ píi, mɛ̀n basↄo mɛ́ è bↄ̀.  
\v 5 Kɛ́ Sili pↄ́ kú Damasi bùsuuↄ mↄ̀ dↄi Adadɛzɛɛlɛ, ↄ̃ Davidi ń gbɛ̃́ↄ dɛ̀dɛ ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bao ń plao (22.000).  
\v 6 À gudↄ̃anaↄ dìlɛdilɛ Sili bùsuu, ↄ̃ aa gↄ̃̀ aà zↄ̀blenaↄ ũ, aaiↄ falubↄɛ̀. Dii tò Davidi zĩblè gu pↄ́ à gɛ̀u píiɛ.  
\v 7 Davidi vua sɛ̀ngbao pↄ́ Adadɛzɛɛ ìwaↄ kũaↄ sɛ̀lɛ tàò Yelusalɛũ.  
\v 8 À mↄgotɛ̃ sɛ̀lɛ zↄ̃ↄzↄ̃ↄ Adadɛzɛɛ wɛ̃́lɛ Teba ń Kunio guu. Salomↄↄ íkakĩi pìò ń mↄ̀pɛlɛↄ ń Lua kpɛ́ pↄ́ↄ. 
\p  
\v 9 Kɛ́ Amata kí Tou mà Davidi zĩblè Zoba kí Adadɛzɛɛ zĩgↄ̃ↄwa píi,  
\v 10 ↄ̃ à a nɛ́ Adolaũ zĩ̀ fↄkpaiwà. À aà sáaukpà zĩ pↄ́ a blè Adadɛzɛɛwa yã́i, asa Tou zĩkàaànↄ yãaɛ. Ɔ̃ Adolaũpi mↄ̀ ń vua pↄ́ↄ ń ã́nusu pↄ́ↄ ń mↄgotɛ̃ pↄ́ↄ,  
\v 11 ↄ̃ kí Davidi dìlɛ Dii pↄ́ ũ, lá a kɛ̀ ń buipãle pↄ́ à gbãablèmáↄ ã́nusuↄ ń vuaↄwa píi, Ɛdↄũↄ ń Mↄabuↄ ń Amↄniↄ ń Filitɛ̃ↄ ń Amalɛki buiↄ.  
\v 12 Zeluia nɛ́ Abisai Ɛdↄũↄ dɛ̀dɛ Guzulɛ Wisideu\f + \fr 18.12 \ft Soũ 60\f* gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bao plasai (18.000).  
\v 13 À gudↄ̃anaↄ dìlɛdilɛ Ɛdↄũ bùsuu lↄ, ↄ̃ Ɛdↄũↄ gↄ̃̀ aà zↄ̀blenaↄ ũ. Dii tò Davidi zĩblè gu pↄ́ à gɛ̀u píiɛ. 
\p  
\v 14 Davidi mɛ́ Isaili bui píi kía ũ, à yãmaa gↄ̃̀gↄ̃ a gbɛ̃́ↄnɛ a zɛ́wa.  
\v 15 Zeluia nɛ́ Yoabu mɛ́ aà zĩgↄ̃ↄ dↄaana ũ. Ailudi nɛ́ Yosafa mɛ́ aà kpàwakɛna ũ.  
\v 16 Aitubu nɛ́ Zadoki ń Abiataa nɛ́ Aimɛlɛkio mɛ́ sa'onkiaↄ ũ. Selaia mɛ́ aà lakɛ̃na ũ.  
\v 17 Yoiada nɛ́ Benaia mɛ́ aà dↄaiↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. Davidipi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ mɛ́ aà kwàasiↄ ũ aà saɛ. 
\c 19  
\s1 Davidi zĩblea Amↄniↄwa 
\r (2Sam 10.1-19) 
\p  
\v 1 Bee gbɛa kɛ́ Amↄniↄ kí Naasa gà, ↄ̃ aà nɛ́ zↄ̃̀lɛ aà gbɛu.  
\v 2 Davidi mɛ̀: Má gbɛ̃kɛkɛ Naasa nɛ́ Anuniɛɛ, kɛ́ aà mae gbɛ̃kɛkɛ̀mɛɛ yãa yã́i. Ɔ̃ Davidi a ìwaeↄ zĩ̀ aa gɛ́ Amↄni bùsuu aa aà nↄ̀sɛ níniɛ̀ aà mae gaa yã́ musu. Kɛ́ Davidi ìwapiↄ kà Anuni kĩ́i we aa aà nↄ̀sɛ níniɛ̀,  
\v 3 ↄ̃ Amↄni kíaↄ ò Anuniɛ: Ńlɛ e Davidi gbɛ̃́ↄ zĩ̀ n mae gɛ̀ kpɛlaa yã́i aà n nↄ̀sɛ níninɛ nɛe? Aa mↄ̀ wá bùsu asiigwaiɛ, aai ɛa mↄ lɛ́lɛwá.  
\v 4 Ɔ̃ Anuni Davidi ìwapiↄ kũ̀kũ à ń lɛkãna wà, à ń pↄkasaↄ zↄ̃̀ɛzↄ̃ɛ a guo an zí lɛ́u, ↄ̃ à ń gbáɛ.  
\v 5 Kɛ́ wà mↄ̀ wa ò Davidiɛ, ↄ̃ à gbɛ̃́ↄ zĩ̀ aa gɛ́ daińlɛ, asa wí ń kṹ maamaaɛ. Aa ònɛ́: Kí mɛ̀ à zↄ̃lɛ Yeliko e á lɛkãna kã́ bↄlɛ, í gbasa su. 
\p  
\v 6 Kɛ́ Anuni ń Amↄniↄ píi è Davidi ye ń gĩyãi lↄo, ↄ̃ aa gbɛ̃́ↄ zĩ̀ Mɛsↄpↄtami bùsuu ń Maaka bùsuo ń Zoba bùsuo ń ã́nusuo tↄnu bla sↄosai, aa fĩaboò zĩkasↄ̃goↄ yã́i.  
\v 7 Ɔ̃ aa fĩabò sↄ̃́go mɛ̀n ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ baakwi ń plao (32.000) ń ń diiↄ yã́ musu. Aa fĩabò Maaka kíaɛ ń a zĩgↄ̃ↄ lↄ. Aa mↄ̀ bòokpà Mɛdeba saɛ, ↄ̃ wà Amↄniↄ kã̀aa wɛ̃́lɛ ń wɛ̃́lɛo, aa gɛ̀ zĩlau.  
\v 8 Kɛ́ Davidi a baomà, ↄ̃ à Yoabu zĩ̀ ń zĩgↄ̃ↄ píi.  
\v 9 Amↄniↄ bↄ̀ zĩ'ↄpòo ń wɛ̃́lɛ bĩ́ibↄlɛu mɛ́ kía pↄ́ mↄ̀piↄ ku sɛ̃u ńtɛ̃ɛ.  
\v 10 Kɛ́ Yoabu è wà zĩ'ↄpòo a aɛ ń a kpɛo, ↄ̃ à Isaili zĩgↄ̃ maaↄ plɛ̀ à ń kálɛ aa gɛ́ lɛ́lɛiɛ Siliↄwa.  
\v 11 À zĩgↄ̃ kĩniↄ nà a dãuna Abisaiɛ a ↄzĩ, à ń kálɛ aa gɛ́ lɛ́lɛi Amↄniↄwa  
\v 12 à mɛ̀: Tó Siliↄ gbãa sù lɛ́ ma fu, mↄ dↄmalɛ. Tó Amↄni buiↄ gbãa mɛ́ sù lɛ́ n fu sↄ̃, má mↄ́ dↄnlɛ.  
\v 13 À sↄ̃dilɛ! Wà gↄ̃ɛkɛ kɛ wá gbɛ̃́ↄ ń wá Dii wɛ̃́lɛↄ yã́ musu. Dii a yã́ pↄ́ kɛ̀ɛ maa kɛ.  
\v 14 Ɔ̃ Yoabu ń zĩgↄ̃ pↄ́ kuanↄↄ gɛ̀ lɛ́ zĩka ń Siliↄ, ↄ̃ Siliↄ bàalɛ̀nɛ́.  
\v 15 Kɛ́ Amↄniↄ è Siliↄ bàalɛ̀, ↄ̃ aa bàalɛ̀ Abisaiɛ sↄ̃, aa sì wɛ̃́lɛ guu, ↄ̃ Yoabu tà Yelusalɛũ. 
\p  
\v 16 Kɛ́ Siliↄ è Isailiↄ zĩblèmá, ↄ̃ aa gbɛ̃́ↄ zĩ̀ Uflata baa, aa gɛ̀ ń gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ nàaa sùńnↄ. Adadɛzɛɛ zĩgↄ̃ↄ dↄaana Sofaki mɛ́ dↄaaa.  
\v 17 Kɛ́ Davidi a baomà, à Isailiↄ kã̀aa píi, ↄ̃ à bùańnↄ Yuudɛ̃wa. Davidi gɛ̀ Siliↄ kĩ́i, à zĩ'ↄpòońzi, ↄ̃ aa sìkↄ̃u.  
\v 18 Aalɛ bàalɛ Isailiↄnɛ, ↄ̃ Davidi ń dɛdɛ sↄ̃́godeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ sopla (7.000) ń kɛ̀sɛdeↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bla (40.000). We wà ń zĩgↄ̃ↄ dↄaana Sofaki dɛ̀u.  
\v 19 Kɛ́ Adadɛzɛɛ zↄ̀blenaↄ è Isailiↄ zĩblèmá màa, ↄ̃ aa lɛdoũkɛ̀ ń Davidio, aa gↄ̃̀ aà zↄ̀blenaↄ ũ. Ɔ̃ Siliↄ i we dↄ̀ Amↄniↄlɛ lↄo. 
\c 20  
\s1 Laba sia Amↄniↄwa 
\r (2Sam 12.26-31) 
\p  
\v 1 Kɛ́ í bↄ̀ ɛu, gↄↄ pↄ́ kíaↄ ì gɛ́ zĩkai, ↄ̃ Yoabu dↄ̀aa zĩgↄ̃ↄnɛ zĩlau. À Amↄni bùsu ásookɛ̀, ↄ̃ à gɛ̀ koezↄ̃̀ Labazi. Gↄↄ bee Davidi ku Yelusalɛũ. Ɔ̃ Yoabu lɛ̀lɛ Labawa a gbòo.  
\v 2 Ɔ̃ Davidi mↄ̀ ń kía vua fùa gò aà miwa. A gbia kà kiloo baakwi, mɛ́ gbɛ̀ bɛɛɛde kuwà. Ɔ̃ wa kpà Davidiɛ. À wɛ̃́lɛpi pↄ́ↄ nàaa dúuduuɛ,  
\v 3 ↄ̃ à gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú weↄ kũ̀kũ bↄ̀lɛńnↄ, à ń dá síi zĩu ń dúuduusu zĩo ń mↄo zĩo. Màa à kɛ̀ Amↄni wɛ̃́lɛↄnɛ píi, ↄ̃ à ɛ̀a tà Yelusalɛũ ń a zĩgↄ̃ↄ píi. 
\s1 Zĩkaa ń Filitɛ̃ↄ 
\r (2Sam 21.15-22) 
\p  
\v 4 Bee gbɛa kɛ́ zĩ̀ fɛ̀lɛ ń Filitɛ̃ↄ Gɛzɛɛ, Usa gbɛ̃́ Sibekai mɛ́ gbɛ̃́ gbã̀a bui pↄ́ wì mɛ Sipai dɛ̀, ↄ̃ Isailiↄ gbãablè Filitɛ̃ↄwa.  
\v 5 Kɛ́ zĩ̀ ɛ̀a fɛ̀lɛ ń Filitɛ̃ↄ lↄ, Yaii nɛ́ Ɛlana mɛ́ Gata gbɛ̃́ Goliati dãuna Lami dɛ̀. Lami sↄ̃mpa dɛ lán zwã̀atãna àsaliwaɛ.  
\v 6 Aalɛ zĩkańnↄ Gata lↄ. Gↄ̃sa tìisie ku we, aà ↄnɛↄ soolosooloɛ, mɛ́ aà gbánɛↄ soolosoolo, apii kɛ̀ baasↄo mɛ̀ndosai, mɛ́ gbɛ̃́ gbã̀a buiɛ lↄ.  
\v 7 À kuabìi Isailiↄwa, ↄ̃ Davidi vĩ̀i Simɛa nɛ́ Yonatãa aà dɛ̀.  
\v 8 Gbɛ̃́piↄá Gata gbɛ̃́ gbã̀a buiↄnɛ. Davidi ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ mɛ́ ń dɛdɛ. 
\c 21  
\s1 Davidi a zĩgↄ̃ↄ naoa 
\r (2Sam 24.1-25) 
\p  
\v 1 Setãu fɛ̀lɛ Isailiↄwa, ↄ̃ à kↄ̃nikɛ̀ Davidiɛ aà Isailiↄ nao.  
\v 2 Ɔ̃ Davidi ò Yoabuɛ ń zĩgↄ̃ dↄaanaↄ: À gɛ Isailiↄ nao za Bɛɛsɛba e à gɛ pɛò Dãwa, í ɛa su ma kĩ́i, kɛ́ mà e ń dasilɛ dↄ̃.  
\v 3 Ɔ̃ Yoabu wèwà à mɛ̀: Dii a gbɛ̃́ↄ kↄ̃nɛ lɛɛ basↄo! Ma dii kí, má dↄ̃ n gbɛ̃́ↄnɛ píi. Àkɛa ń ye kɛ màai? Bↄ́yãi ń ye yã'i Isailiↄnɛi?  
\v 4 Ń beeo kí yã́ Yoabu blè, ↄ̃ à bↄ̀ gɛ̀ Isaili bùsu kɛ̀ɛlɛ, à ɛ̀a sù Yelusalɛũ.  
\v 5 Ɔ̃ Yoabu gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ a ń naoↄ lɛ́ ò Davidiɛ. Isaili bùsu guu píi gↄ̃ɛ pↄ́ aa fɛ̃nda dↄ̃ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn miliↄ̃ do ń ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ basↄooɛ (1.100.000). Yudaↄ sↄ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ ↄ̀aa pla ń bàaↄ̃kwioɛ (470.000).  
\v 6 Yoabu i Levii buiↄ ń Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ da nao guuo, asa yã́ pↄ́ kí dàɛpi i kaaàguo. 
\p  
\v 7 Yã́ pↄ́ Davidi kɛ̀pi kɛ̀ Luaɛ ĩ́i, ↄ̃ à ↄtↄ̃̀ Isailiↄwa.  
\v 8 Ɔ̃ Davidi ò Luaɛ: Ma duunakɛ̀ maamaa yã́pi kɛa guu. Mapi n zↄ̀blena, ma tàae kɛ̃a sa, asa ma sↄũyã kɛ̀ɛ.  
\v 9 Dii yã'ò Davidi gu'ena Gadaɛ à mɛ̀:  
\v 10 Gɛ ǹ o Davidiɛ ma mɛ̀ má yã́ mɛ̀n àaↄ̃ kpaaĩɛ̀. Aà yã́ mɛ̀ndo sɛ a guu, mí kɛɛ̀.  
\v 11 Ɔ̃ Gada gɛ̀ Davidi lè a òɛ̀: Dii mɛ̀ yã́ɛ beeↄ do gwa ǹ sɛ́.  
\v 12 Imina wɛ̃̀ àaↄ̃ ge bàalɛa n ibɛɛↄnɛ á dɛdɛa ń fɛ̃ndao mↄ àaↄ̃ ge Dii Malaika gagyãkaa Isaili bùsu gupiiu gↄↄ àaↄ̃ Dii fɛ̃nda ũ. A kpele ń sɛ̀i? Gwa ǹ sɛ́, mí dↄ̃ lá má gɛ́ o ma Zĩnaɛ.  
\v 13 Ɔ̃ Davidi ò Gadaɛ: Má kú yeelɛa zↄ̃ↄ guuɛ. Má sì wà lɛ́lɛ da Dii ↄzĩ, asa a sósobi vĩ maamaaɛ. Asu to mà lɛ́lɛ da gbɛ̃nazĩna ↄzĩo.  
\v 14 Ɔ̃ Dii gagyãkà Isailiↄgu, ↄ̃ Isailiↄ gàga gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bàaↄ̃kwi (70.000).  
\v 15 Ɔ̃ Lua malaikae zĩ̀ aà gɛ́ yã́yiai Yelusalɛũdeↄwa. Gↄↄ pↄ́ àlɛ ń dɛdɛ, ↄ̃ Dii a nↄ̀sɛ suumpà an dɛdɛapi yã́ musu, ↄ̃ a ò malaika pↄ́ lɛ́ ń dɛdɛpiɛ: Zɛ màa! Ǹ n ↄ sↄaa sa. Yebusi bui Alauna pↄ́wɛngbɛ̃zɛa ↄ̃ Dii Malaikapi kuu.  
\v 16 Kɛ́ Davidi wɛzù, ↄ̃ à malaikapi è zɛa gugbↄ̃u a musu yã́io a zĩ́lɛ yã́io, à a fɛ̃nda ↄ pooa Yelusalɛũa. Ɔ̃ Davidi ń gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ wùlɛ ń gbɛɛu zwã̀nkasaↄ kákaańla.  
\v 17 Ɔ̃ Davidi ò Luaɛ: Mámɛ má ò wà gbɛ̃́ↄ nao. Mámɛ ma duunapi kɛ̀ ma tàaekɛ̀. Gbɛ̃́piↄá ma kpàsa sãↄnɛ. Aai yãe kɛo. Dii ma Lua, to n ↄ sua ń ma de bɛdeↄ. Ńsu ǹ n gbɛ̃́ↄ dɛdɛ ń gagyãpioo. 
\p  
\v 18 Ɔ̃ Dii Malaikapi ò Gadaɛ aà o Davidiɛ aà gɛ́ Dii gbagbakĩi boi Yebusi bui Alauna pↄ́wɛngbɛ̃zɛu.  
\v 19 Ɔ̃ Davidi gɛ̀ lá Gada òɛ ń Dii tↄ́o kɛi.  
\v 20 Alauna lɛ́ ése gbɛ̃. Kɛ́ à lìli, à malaikapi è. Aà nɛ́ gbɛ̃ↄn síiↄ̃ pↄ́ kuaànↄↄ bↄ̀zã.  
\v 21 Kɛ́ Alauna gugwà, a è Davidi lɛ́ mↄ́ a kĩ́i, ↄ̃ à bↄ̀ pↄ́wɛngbɛ̃zɛa, à gɛ̀ kùlɛ Davidiɛ à wùlɛ a gbɛɛu.  
\v 22 Ɔ̃ Davidi òɛ̀: Ǹ n pↄ́wɛngbɛ̃zɛ yíaa mà Dii gbagbakĩi bou, kɛ́ gagyãpi e go gbɛ̃́ↄla. Yíaa a ↄ̃awa.  
\v 23 Ɔ̃ Alauna ò Davidiɛ: Sɛ́! Ma dii kí, lá à kɛ̀nɛ maa, kɛò. Gwa, má zuↄ kpa sa'obↄ ũ ń pↄ́wɛngbɛ̃goↄ yàa ũ ń éseo pↄ́wɛn gba ũ. Má n gba píiɛ.  
\v 24 Ɔ̃ kí Davidi òɛ̀: Aawo! Má lúmáɛ, mí a fĩabonɛ píi. Má pↄ́ pↄ́ dɛ n pↄ́ ũ sɛ mà kpa Diiwao. Má sa'oowà pã fĩabosaio.  
\v 25 Ɔ̃ à pↄ́wɛngbɛ̃zɛpi lùwà vua ↄwatɛ̃ mɛ̀n ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃.  
\v 26 À Dii gbagbakĩi bò we, ↄ̃ à sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ òwà ń sáaukpasao. Kɛ́ à lɛzù Diizi, ↄ̃ Dii wèwà à tɛ́ gbàɛ za musu, à sù gbagbakĩipiwa. 
\p  
\v 27 Dii yã'ò malaikapiɛ, ↄ̃ à a fɛ̃nda sↄ̀lↄ a kpɛ́u.  
\v 28 Kɛ́ Davidi è Dii sìanↄ Yebusi bui Alauna pↄ́wɛngbɛ̃zɛa, ↄ̃ à ɛ̀a sa'òwà we lↄ.  
\v 29 Gↄↄ bee Dii zwã̀akpɛ pↄ́ Mↄizi kɛ̀ guwaiwaiu ń a gbagbakĩio ku Gabaↄ̃ↄ gulɛsĩ pↄ́ wa bòu.  
\v 30 Davidi lí fↄ̃ gɛ̀ yãgbɛai Diiwa weo, asa àlɛ vĩakɛ Dii malaika fɛ̃ndaɛɛ. 
\c 22  
\p  
\v 1 Ɔ̃ Davidi mɛ̀: Lakĩi Dii Lua kpɛ́ aↄ kuu ń sa pↄ́ Isailiↄ ì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ okĩio. 
\s1 Lua kpɛ́ dↄa sↄukɛa 
\p  
\v 2 Davidi ò wà bↄ̀mↄ pↄ́ kú Isaili bùsuuↄ kãaa píi, ↄ̃ à ń gbɛ̃eↄ dìlɛ gbɛ̀'ãnaↄ ũ aa gbɛↄ ã wà Lua kpɛ́ boò.  
\v 3 À mↄ kpà siaↄwa maamaa aa kusaↄ ń sanɛɛↄ kɛò gãmↄↄ ń bↄlɛↄ pↄ́ ũ. Mↄgotɛ̃ pↄ́ a kpà sↄ̃, à gɛ̃̀ oaa.  
\v 4 Sɛdɛ lí pↄ́ a kpàↄ dasi, wa a lɛ́ dↄ̃o, asa Sidↄ̃deↄ ń Tiideↄ mↄ̀ɛ̀ ń sɛdɛ líↄ à kɛ̀ zài.  
\v 5 Davidi mɛ̀: Ma nɛ́ Salomↄↄá ɛ̀waasonaɛ, a yãe yáasi dↄ̃ gĩao. À kũ̀ kpɛ́ pↄ́ wa dↄ Diiɛ aↄ zↄ̃ↄɛ, i ɛa aↄ kɛfɛũ lↄ maamaa, gbɛ̃́pii i a maabo. A yã́i tò málɛ a dↄa sↄukɛ. Ɔ̃ Davidi kpɛ́pi dↄa sↄukɛ̀ maamaa e àↄ gɛ́ gai. 
\p  
\v 6 Ɔ̃ à a nɛ́ Salomↄↄ sìsi, a òɛ̀ aà kpɛdↄ Dii Isailiↄ Luaɛ.  
\v 7 A òɛ̀: Ma nɛ́, ma zɛò ma sↄ̃ guu mà kpɛdↄ Dii ma Luaɛ, aà tↄ́ iↄ kuwà.  
\v 8 Ɔ̃ Dii yã'òmɛɛ à mɛ̀ ma gbɛ̃dɛ̀dɛ dasi zĩ pↄ́ má kàↄ guu. Má e kpɛ́pi dↄɛo gbɛ̃́ dasi pↄ́ ma ń dɛdɛ a aɛ yã́i.  
\v 9 À mɛ̀ nɛ́ pↄ́ má i mɛ́ aↄ dɛ aafia gbɛ̃́ ũ, asa á tó aà kã́mabo aà ibɛɛ pↄ́ liaiↄ yã́ musuɛ. Wa tↄ́kpa nɛ́piɛ Salomↄↄ.\f + \fr 22.9 \ft Bee mɛ̀ aafia.\f* À mɛ̀ á tó Isailiↄ kua àↄ na kílikili aà gↄↄɛ.  
\v 10 Aàpi mɛ́ a kpɛdↄɛ, iↄ dɛ a nɛ́ ũ, íↄ dɛ aà mae ũ. Á aà zↄ̃lɛa kpalau Isailiↄ guu zɛdↄ, aà kpala aↄ láaa vĩo.  
\v 11 Tia sↄ̃ ma nɛ́, Dii aↄ kunnↄ, i n daɛ ń gòmio, ní kpɛdↄ Dii n Luapiɛ, lá a ò n yã́ musuwa.  
\v 12 Dii n gba ↄ̃nↄ ń wɛzɛ̃o gↄↄ pↄ́ a n dilɛ Isailiↄnɛ, kɛ́ ǹyↄ̃ aà ikoyã kũa.  
\v 13 Tó ń ikoyã pↄ́ Dii dà Mↄiziɛ a dìlɛ Isailiↄnɛ kũa, mɛ́ ńlɛ aà ↄtondↄkĩi gwa, ńyↄ̃ kã́fĩa e. Sↄ̃dilɛ, níↄ wↄ́ↄ vĩ. Ńsu to vĩa n kũo. Ńsu to sↄ̃ kɛ̃nguo. 
\p  
\v 14 Ma dɛ̃ɛkà ma vua kàlɛ Dii kpɛ́ pↄ́ ũ tↄnu ↄ̀aa gɛ̃o ń plao, ã́nusu sↄ̃ tↄnu ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ baakwi ń síiↄ̃o. Mↄ́ ń mↄgotɛ̃o sↄ̃, wa a lɛ́ dↄ̃o, a gbia kɛ̀ zài. Ma lí ń gbɛo kàlɛ we lↄ. Pↄ́piↄ kã́fĩ lↄ.  
\v 15 Ń zĩkɛnaↄ vĩ dasi, gbɛ̀'ãnaↄ ń li'ãnaↄ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ gↄ̃i vĩ ↄzĩ píi guuↄ,  
\v 16 vua zĩ, ã́nusu zĩ, mↄgotɛ̃ zĩ ń mↄsi zĩo. N ↄzĩkɛnaↄ lɛ́ vĩo. Na zĩpiwa! Dii aↄ kunnↄ! 
\p  
\v 17 Ɔ̃ Davidi ò Isaili kíaↄnɛ aa mↄ dↄ a nɛ́ Salomↄↄlɛ  
\v 18 à mɛ̀: Dii á Lua kúánↄo lé? I á gba ĩ́ampakĩi gupiiuo lé? À gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú bùsuɛ beeu za káauↄ nàmɛɛ ma ↄzĩɛ, ↄ̃ bùsupi gↄ̃̀ Diipi ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ pↄ́ ũ sa.  
\v 19 À Dii á Lua kĩ́i wɛɛlɛ teasisai ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo sa, í na Dii Lua kúkĩi boawa, í su ń Dii bàakuaánↄ kpagoloo ń aà pↄ́ keleↄ kpɛ́ pↄ́ álɛ dↄɛ̀, aà tↄ́ iↄ kuwàpi guu. 
\c 23  
\p  
\v 1 Kɛ́ Davidi zikũ̀ táotao, ↄ̃ à Salomↄↄ kpà Isailiↄ kía ũ.\f + \fr 23.1 \ft 1Kia 1.38-39\f* 
\s1 Levii buiↄ zĩ 
\p  
\v 2 Davidi Isaili kíaↄ kã̀aa ń sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ píi.  
\v 3 Wà Levii bui gↄ̃ɛ pↄ́ kà wɛ̃̀ baakwi ge aa dɛaↄ nào, aa gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ bla plasaiɛ (38.000).  
\v 4 Ɔ̃ Davidi gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ baasↄo mɛ̀ndosaiↄ (24.000) dìlɛ aaↄ wɛ́tɛ Dii ua yã́ↄi, à gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ sooloↄ (6.000) dìlɛ lakɛ̃naↄ ń yãgↄ̃gↄ̃naↄ ũ.  
\v 5 Ɔ̃ à gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ síiↄ̃ↄ (4.000) dìlɛ bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ũ, mɛ́ à gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ síiↄ̃ↄ (4.000) dìlɛ Dii táasilɛnaↄ ũ, aaliↄ aà táasilɛ ń pↄ́'ↄbↄna pↄ́ Davidi kpàↄ.  
\v 6 Davidi ń kpaalɛ̀ ń buiↄwa gã ń gão, Geesↄ̃ buiↄ, Kɛata buiↄ ń Mɛlali buiↄ. 
\p  
\v 7 Geesↄ̃ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Ladã ń Simɛio ũ.  
\v 8 Ladã nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ àaↄ̃ɛ: A sɛ̃́ia Yeiɛli, a gbɛa Zetaũ ń Yoɛlio.  
\v 9 Simɛi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ àaↄ̃ɛ: Selomↄ, Haziɛli ń Halanao. Ladã bui uabele káauↄn we.  
\v 10 Simɛi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ síiↄ̃ɛ: Yaata, Ziza, Yeusi ń Bɛliao.  
\v 11 A sɛ̃́ia Yaata, a plaade Ziza. Yeusi ń Bɛliao buiↄ dasio, ↄ̃ wà ń dílɛ bui doũ zĩ doũ guu. 
\p  
\v 12 Kɛata nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ síiↄ̃ɛ: Amlaũ, Isaa, Hɛblↄ̃ ń Uziɛlio.  
\v 13 Amlaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Aalona ń Mↄizio ũ. Wà Aalona ń a buiↄ dìlɛ ń zɛ́i, aaↄ laaidↄ Lua pↄ́ↄwa, aaↄ Luapi gbagba, aaↄ tulaletikatɛaɛ̀, aaↄ zĩkɛ aà kúkĩi, aaↄ samaa'o gbɛ̃́ↄnɛ ń aà tↄ́o gↄↄpii.\f + \fr 23.13 \ft Bↄa 28.1\f* 
\v 14 Wà Lua gbɛ̃́ Mↄizi buiↄ dìlɛ lán Levii bui kĩniↄwa.  
\v 15 Mↄizi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Geesoũ ń Ɛliɛzɛɛo ũ.  
\v 16 Geesoũ nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ian Sebuɛli ũ.  
\v 17 Ɛliɛzɛɛ nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ian Lɛabia ũ. I nɛgↄ̃ɛe i lↄo, ãma Lɛabiapi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ì dasi maamaaɛ. 
\p  
\v 18 Isaa nɛgↄ̃ɛ sɛ̃́ian Selomi ũ.  
\v 19 Hɛblↄ̃ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: A sɛ̃́ia Yelia, a plaade Amalia, a àaↄ̃de Yaaziɛ, a síiↄ̃de Yekamaũ.  
\v 20 Uziɛli nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: A sɛ̃́ia Mika, a plaade Isia. 
\p  
\v 21 Mɛlali nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Mali ń Musio ũ. Mali nɛgↄ̃ɛↄn Ɛleazaa ń Kisio ũ.  
\v 22 Ɛleazaa gà nɛgↄ̃ɛsaiɛ, nɛnↄɛↄ a ì tɛ̃ɛtɛ̃ɛ. An desɛ̃ Kisi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ mɛ́ ń sɛsɛ.  
\v 23 Musi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ àaↄ̃ɛ: Mali ń Edɛɛo ń Yelemↄo. 
\p  
\v 24 Levii buiↄn we sɛa an dezi pↄ́ dɛ uabele káau ũↄwa. Lua ua zĩkɛna pↄ́ kà wɛ̃̀ bao ge aa dɛaↄ, wà ń baade tↄ́ dàlau an buipiↄwaɛ.  
\v 25 Davidi mɛ̀: Lá Dii Isailiↄ Lua a gbɛ̃́ↄ gbà ĩ́ampakĩi mɛ́ à sù Yelusalɛũ àↄ ku we gↄↄpiiɛ,  
\v 26 Levii buiↄ zwã̀akpɛ ń a zĩkɛbↄↄ sɛ táa'oò lↄo.  
\v 27 Yã́ pↄ́ Davidi ò gbɛzã yã́i ↄ̃ wì Levii bui pↄ́ kà wɛ̃̀ bao ge aa dɛaↄ naoi. 
\p  
\v 28 Levii buipiↄ líↄ dↄ Aalona buiↄlɛ ń Dii ua zĩo. Aaliↄ wɛ́tɛ Lua uai ń a kpɛ́ↄ ń gbãbↄa Lua pↄ́ↄnɛↄ ń zĩ pↄ́ wì kɛ weo  
\v 29 ń pɛ̃ɛ pↄ́ wì kpa Luawao ń pↄ́wɛnti gbao ń kàawanao ń a totoao ń a zaao ń a zↄ̃ↄ lɛ́o.  
\v 30 Aaliↄ Dii sáaukpa ń aà táasilɛao kↄↄ ń oosio  
\v 31 ń gↄↄ pↄ́ wàlɛ sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ o Diiwa kã́mabogↄↄzĩↄ ń mↄ gↄↄ sɛ̃́ia zĩ́ↄ ń dikpɛ pↄ́ wa dìlɛↄ. Aaliↄ zĩkɛ Diiɛ gↄↄpii màa, mɛ́ an dasi lí ká lá wa dìlɛnɛ́wa.  
\v 32 Ampiↄ mɛ́ aali laaidↄ kpaaũkpɛ ń a pↄkeleↄ zĩwa, mɛ́ an gbɛ̃́ Aalona buiↄ lí laaidↄ Dii kpɛ́ zĩwa.\f + \fr 23.32 \ft Nao 3.5-9\f* 
\c 24  
\s1 Sa'onaↄ zĩ 
\p  
\v 1 Aalona bui gãliↄn kɛ: Aalona nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Nadabu, Abiu, Ɛleazaa ń Itamaao.  
\v 2 Nadabu ń Abiuo gàga ń mae wáaɛ,\f + \fr 24.2 \ft Lev 10.1-2\f* aai nɛgↄ̃ɛ i sↄ̃o. Ɔ̃ Ɛleazaa ń Itamaao gↄ̃̀ sa'onaↄ ũ.  
\v 3 Davidi ń Ɛleazaa bui Zadokio ń Itamaa bui Aimɛlɛkio sa'onaↄ kpaalɛ̀ gã ń gão, aaↄ kↄ̃ gba zɛ́ zĩ yã́ musu.  
\v 4 Aa dↄaanaↄ è dasi Ɛleazaa buiↄ guu dɛ Itamaa buiↄ guula, ↄ̃ aa Ɛleazaa bui uabeleↄ sɛ̀ gbɛ̃ↄn gɛ̃o ń mɛ̀ndoo, Itamaa bui uabeleↄ sↄ̃ swaaↄ̃.  
\v 5 Aa ń kpaalɛ̀ ń gbɛlaaoɛ an wɛgwasai, asa Ɛleazaa buieↄ ń Itamaa buieↄ dɛ Lua kpɛ́ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ ń sa'onkiaↄ ũ ḿpiiɛ.  
\v 6 Levii bui lakɛ̃na Semaia, Nɛtanɛli nɛ́ ń tↄ́ dàlau kía ń aà ìwaɛ beeↄ wáaɛ: Sa'onkia Zadoki, Abiataa nɛ́ Aimɛlɛki, sa'ona uabeleↄ ń Levii bui uabeleↄ. Tó wà gbɛ̃́ sɛ̀ Ɛleazaa bui guu do, ↄ̃ wì sɛ Itamaa bui guu do. 
\q1  
\v 7 Yoialibu mɛ́ sɛ̃́ia, 
\q1 a plaade Yedaia, 
\q1  
\v 8 a àaↄ̃de Aliũ, 
\q1 a síiↄ̃de Seoliũ, 
\q1  
\v 9 a sↄode Malakia, 
\q1 a soolode Miamɛ, 
\q1  
\v 10 a soplade Akozi, 
\q1 a swaaↄ̃de Abia, 
\q1  
\v 11 a kɛ̃okwide Yesua, 
\q1 a kwide Sekania, 
\q1  
\v 12 a kuɛdode Ɛliasibu, 
\q1 a kuɛplade Yakiũ, 
\q1  
\v 13 a kuɛ'aaↄ̃de Hupa, 
\q1 a gɛ̃o mɛ̀ndosaide Yɛsɛba, 
\q1  
\v 14 a gɛ̃ode Bilega, 
\q1 a gɛ̃o ń mɛ̀ndoode Imɛɛ, 
\q1  
\v 15 a gɛ̃o ń plaode Ezii, 
\q1 a bao plasaide Apisɛsi, 
\q1  
\v 16 a bao mɛ̀ndosaide Petaia, 
\q1 a baode Yeezekɛli, 
\q1  
\v 17 a bao ń mɛ̀ndoode Yakɛ̃, 
\q1 a bao ń plaode Gamulu, 
\q1  
\v 18 a bao ń àaↄ̃ode Delaia, 
\q1 a baasↄo mɛ̀ndosaide Maazia. 
\m  
\v 19 Lá aali gɛ́ zĩkɛi Dii kpɛ́u aaↄ kↄ̃ gba zɛ́n we, lá Dii Isailiↄ Lua dà an dezi Aalonaɛ a dìlɛwa. 
\s1 Levii bui kĩniↄ 
\p  
\v 20 Levii bui kĩniↄn kɛ: Amlaũ bui Sebuɛli nɛ́ Yedeia. 
\p  
\v 21 Lɛabia yoa Isia. 
\p  
\v 22 Isaa bui Selomↄ nɛ́ Yaata. 
\p  
\v 23 Hɛblↄ̃ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Yelia, Amalia, Yaaziɛ ń Yekamaũo. 
\p  
\v 24 Uziɛli bui Mika nɛ́ Samii. 
\p  
\v 25 Mika dãuna Isia nɛ́ Zakali. 
\p  
\v 26 Mɛlali nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ Mali ń Musio.  
\v 27 Mɛlali bui Yaazia nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Bɛnↄ, Soaũ, Zakuu ń Ibelio.  
\v 28 Mali nɛ́ Ɛleazaa i nɛgↄ̃ɛ io.  
\v 29 Mali nɛ́ Kisi bui Yelamɛli.  
\v 30 Musi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Mali, Edɛɛ ń Yelimↄo. Levii buiↄn we an dezi buiↄwa. 
\p  
\v 31 Ampiↄ sↄ̃ aa gbɛlà lá an gbɛ̃́ Aalona buiↄ kɛ̀wa kí Davidi ń Zadokio ń Aimɛlɛkio ń sa'ona uabeleↄ ń Levii bui uabeleↄ wáaɛ. Vĩ̀i buiↄ ń dãuna buiↄ, yã́ doũ wa kɛ̀nɛ́. 
\c 25  
\s1 Lɛ̀sinaↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Davidi ń Isaili kíaↄ mɛ́ Asafa nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ń Emani nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ń Yedutu nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ dìlɛ ń zɛ́i aa ãnabikɛkɛ ń mↄↄnaↄ ń domaↄ ń sɛ̃́sɛ̃naↄ. Zĩpikɛnaↄ tↄ́n kɛ: 
\p  
\v 2 Asafa nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Zakuu, Yosɛfu, Nɛtania ń Asalɛlao. Asafa mɛ́ aↄ wɛ́tɛ a nɛ́piↄzi, kía sↄ̃ iↄ wɛ́tɛ ń ãnabikɛkɛai. 
\p  
\v 3 Yedutu nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ sooloɛ: Gedalia, Zeli, Yesaia, Simɛi, Asabia ń Matitiao. An mae Yedutu mɛ́ ìↄ wɛ́tɛńzi, ↄ̃ ìↄ ãnabikɛkɛ ń mↄↄnlɛao, ìↄ Dii sáau kpa àↄ aà táasilɛò. 
\p  
\v 4 Emani nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: Bukia, Matania, Uziɛli, Sebuɛli, Yelemↄ, Anania, Anani, Ɛliata, Gidaleti, Lomantiɛzɛɛ, Maloti, Yↄsebekasa, Otii ń Maazioo.  
\v 5 Gbɛ̃́piↄá kí gu'ena Emani nɛgↄ̃ɛↄnɛ ḿpii. Lua lɛgbɛ̃̀ɛ̀ à mɛ̀ á aà gba gbãa, ↄ̃ à aà gbà nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ gɛ̃o mɛ̀ndosai ń nɛnↄɛↄ lↄ àaↄ̃.  
\v 6 Gbɛ̃́piↄ ìↄ lɛsi Dii ua ń sɛ̃́sɛ̃naↄ ń domaↄ ń mↄↄnaↄ ḿpiiɛ. An maeↄ Asafa ń Yedutuo ń Emanio mɛ́ aaìↄ wɛ́tɛńzi Lua ua zĩpi guu. Kí sↄ̃ ìↄ wɛ́tɛ ń maepiↄzi.  
\v 7 Ampiↄ ń ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa lɛsia Diiɛ dàda aa dↄ̃ↄ, ampii gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa do ń basiiↄ̃kwi plasaioɛ (288).  
\v 8 Wà likpà lá aali kↄ̃ gba zɛ́ zĩpi yã́ musuɛ, nɛ́fɛ̃nɛn gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ, yãdanɛdeↄ ń yãdadanaↄ píi.  
\v 9 Wà gbɛ̃́piↄ sɛ̀ baade ń a nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ń a dãunaↄ gbɛ̃ↄn kuɛplaplaɛ: 
\q1 A sɛ̃́ia Asafa nɛ́ Yosɛfu, 
\q1 a plaade Gedalia, 
\q1  
\v 10 a àaↄ̃de Zakuu, 
\q1  
\v 11 a síiↄ̃de Zeli, 
\q1  
\v 12 a sↄode Nɛtania, 
\q1  
\v 13 a soolode Bukia, 
\q1  
\v 14 a soplade Yesalela, 
\q1  
\v 15 a swaaↄ̃de Yesaia, 
\q1  
\v 16 a kɛ̃okwide Matania, 
\q1  
\v 17 a kwide Simɛi, 
\q1  
\v 18 a kuɛdode Azalɛli, 
\q1  
\v 19 a kuɛplade Asabia, 
\q1  
\v 20 a kuɛ'aaↄ̃de Sebuɛli, 
\q1  
\v 21 a gɛ̃o mɛ̀ndosaide Matitia, 
\q1  
\v 22 a gɛ̃ode Yelimↄ, 
\q1  
\v 23 a gɛ̃o ń mɛ̀ndoode Anania, 
\q1  
\v 24 a gɛ̃o ń plaode Yↄsebekasa, 
\q1  
\v 25 a bao plasaide Anani, 
\q1  
\v 26 a bao mɛ̀ndosaide Maloti, 
\q1  
\v 27 a baode Ɛliata, 
\q1  
\v 28 a bao ń mɛ̀ndoode Otii, 
\q1  
\v 29 a bao ń plaode Gidaleti, 
\q1  
\v 30 a bao ń àaↄ̃ode Maazio, 
\q1  
\v 31 a baasↄo mɛ̀ndosaide Lomantiɛzɛɛ. 
\c 26  
\s1 Lua kpɛ bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ gãliↄn kɛ: 
\q1 Sɛ̃́ia Kole buiↄ. 
\q1 Kole nɛ́ Mɛsɛlɛmia, Abiasafa tↄũna. 
\q1  
\v 2 Mɛsɛlɛmia nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: 
\q1 A sɛ̃́ia Zakali, 
\q1 a plaade Yediaɛ, 
\q1 a àaↄ̃de Zebadia, 
\q1 a síiↄ̃de Yaniɛli, 
\q1  
\v 3 a sↄode Elaũ, 
\q1 a soolode Yohanani, 
\q1 a soplade Ɛlioenai. 
\q1  
\v 4 Ɔbɛdɛdↄũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: 
\q1 A sɛ̃́ia Semaia, 
\q1 a plaade Yozaba, 
\q1 a àaↄ̃de Yoa, 
\q1 a síiↄ̃de Sakaa, 
\q1 a sↄode Nɛtanɛli, 
\q1  
\v 5 a soolode Amiɛli, 
\q1 a soplade Isakaa, 
\q1 a swaaↄ̃de Puletai. 
\m Asa Lua mɛ́ ɛ̀fãaikɛ̀ Ɔbɛdɛdↄũpiɛ.\f + \fr 26.5 \ft 1Lad 13.14\f* 
\v 6 Aà nɛ́ Semaia nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ì lↄ, aa kpalablè ń dezi buiↄ guu, asa bɛɛɛdeↄnɛ.  
\v 7 Semaia nɛ́piↄn kɛ: Ɔtɛni, Lefaɛli, Ɔbɛdi ń Ɛlizabao. Aà dãunaↄ Ɛlihu ń Semakiaoá bɛɛɛdeↄnɛ lↄ.  
\v 8 Gbɛ̃́piↄá Ɔbɛdɛdↄũ buiↄnɛ ḿpii. Ampiↄ ń ń nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ń ń dãunaↄá bɛɛɛdeↄnɛ, an gbãa kà zĩpi kɛa. Aa gbɛ̃ↄn bàaↄ̃ ń plaoɛ.  
\v 9 Mɛsɛlɛmia nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ń a dãunaↄá bɛɛɛdeↄnɛ lↄ. Aa gbɛ̃ↄn bao plasaiɛ. 
\p  
\v 10 Mɛlali bui Osa nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ tↄ́n kɛ: A sɛ̃́ia Simɛli, ãma nɛ́ sɛ̃́ia no, aà mae mɛ́ aà dìlɛ yoa ũ.  
\v 11 A plaade Ilikia, a àaↄ̃de Tabalia, a síiↄ̃de Zakali. Osa nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ń a dãunaↄ gbɛ̃ↄn kuɛ'aaↄ̃ɛ. 
\p  
\v 12 Wà zĩdà bui dↄaanapiↄnɛ, baade ń a bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃an gãliↄ, lá wa dà ń daɛ pↄ́ lɛ́ zĩkɛ Dii uaↄnɛwa.  
\v 13 Wà likpànɛ́ ń buiwaɛ, nɛ́fɛ̃nɛn gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ń bↄlɛ pↄ́ an baade aↄ dↄ̃́ao.  
\v 14 Mɛsɛlɛmia gukpɛ oi bↄlɛ blè, ↄ̃ aà nɛ́ Zakali pↄ́ dɛ lɛdamade ↄ̃nↄna ũ gugbãntoo oi bↄlɛ blè.  
\v 15 Ɔbɛdɛdↄũ gɛↄmidↄkĩi oi bↄlɛ blè, mɛ́ aà nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ mɛ́ dↄ̃ↄ dↄ̃́aa blè.  
\v 16 Osa bɛ'aɛ oi bↄlɛ blè ń zɛda pↄ́ kú musu bↄlɛ pↄ́ wì mɛ Salɛkɛ Bↄlɛo. 
\p Bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃anaↄ ìↄ kↄ̃ lɛũkpakɛɛ.  
\v 17 Levii buipiↄ ìↄ ku gukpɛ oi lá gu lɛ́ dↄ gbɛ̃ↄn soolosoolo, gugbãntoo oi gbɛ̃ↄn síiↄ̃siiↄ̃, gɛↄmidↄkĩi oi gbɛ̃ↄn síiↄ̃siiↄ̃, dↄ̃ↄ saɛ gbɛ̃ↄn plapla.  
\v 18 Bɛ'aɛ oi gbɛ̃ↄn síiↄ̃siiↄ̃ ìↄ ku zɛdau, ua oi sↄ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn plapla.  
\v 19 Kole buiↄ ń Mɛlali bui bĩ́ibↄlɛdↄ̃ana gãliↄn we. 
\s1 Làasi dↄ̃̀anaↄ ń yãgↄ̃gↄ̃naↄ 
\p  
\v 20 An gbɛ̃́ Levii buiↄ mɛ́ Lua kpɛ́ làasiↄ ń pↄ́ pↄ́ wì Lua gba làasiↄ dↄ̃̀anaↄ ũ.  
\v 21 Geesↄ̃ bui Ladã bui uabeleↄn kɛ: Yeiɛli  
\v 22 ń a nɛ́ Zetaũo ń Zetaũpi dãuna Yoɛlio. Ampiↄ mɛ́ aaìↄ wɛ́tɛ Dii kpɛ́ làasiↄi. 
\p  
\v 23 Amlaũ bui gbɛ̃eↄ ń Isaa bui gbɛ̃eↄ ń Hɛblↄ̃ bui gbɛ̃eↄ ń Uziɛli bui gbɛ̃eↄ ku we lↄ. Ampiↄn kɛ:  
\v 24 Mↄizi nɛ́ Geesoũ bui Sebuɛli mɛ́ làasi gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ.  
\v 25 Aà deziↄ do Ɛleazaa mɛ́ Lɛabia ì, Lɛabia Yesaia ì, Yesaia Yolaũ ì, Yolaũ Zikeli ì, Zikeli Selomi ì.  
\v 26 Selomipi ń a daɛↄ mɛ́ pↄ́ pↄ́ wa Lua gbà làasiↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ ũ. Kí Davidi ń uabele pↄ́ dɛ zĩgↄ̃ dↄaanaↄ ũↄ mɛ́ gbapiↄ dà.  
\v 27 Aa pↄ́ pↄ́ aa nàaa zĩ guuↄ kpà Luawa wà aà kpɛ́ kɛkɛò.  
\v 28 Selomi ń a daɛↄ mɛ́ aaìↄ wɛ́tɛ pↄ́ pↄ́ gu'ena Samuɛli ń Kisi nɛ́ Sauluo ń Nɛɛ nɛ́ Abinɛɛo ń Zeluia nɛ́ Yoabuo kpàↄi ń pↄ́ pↄ́ gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ kpàↄ píi. 
\p  
\v 29 Wà bàasi zĩ dà Isaa bui Kenaniaɛ ń a nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ. Aamɛ Isailiↄ lakɛ̃naↄ ń ń yãgↄ̃gↄ̃naↄ ũ.  
\v 30 Hɛblↄ̃ bui Asabia ń a daɛↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa swaaↄ̃ ń basↄooɛ (1.700). Bɛɛɛdeↄnɛ ḿpii. Aaìↄ wɛ́tɛ Isaili bùsu pↄ́ kú Yuudɛ̃ baa bɛ'aɛzi Dii yã́ musu ń zĩ pↄ́ kí dànɛ́ yã́ musuo píi.  
\v 31 Yelia mɛ́ Hɛblↄ̃ buiↄ kía ũ. Davidi kpalablea wɛ̃̀ blade guu ↄ̃ à wɛtɛ̀tɛ Hɛblↄ̃ buipi tↄ́ pↄ́ wa kà láuↄzi, ↄ̃ wà gɛ̀ bↄ̀ an bɛɛɛdeↄwa an bɛ wɛ̃́lɛu Yazɛɛ, Galada bùsuu.  
\v 32 Yelia daɛ uabeleↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aa kuɛ'aaↄ̃ ń basↄooɛ (2.700). Bɛɛɛdeↄnɛ ḿpii, ↄ̃ kí Davidi ń dílɛ aaↄ wɛ́tɛ Lubɛni buiↄzi ń Gada buiↄ ń Manase bui pↄ́ kú gukpɛ oi weↄ Lua yã́ ń azĩa yã́o kɛkɛa yã́i. 
\c 27  
\s1 Zĩgↄ̃ↄ 
\p  
\v 1 Isaili uabeleↄ ń zĩgↄ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄoↄ dↄaanaↄ ń zĩgↄ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn basↄobasↄoↄ dↄaanaↄ ń ń lakɛ̃na pↄ́ aaìↄ zĩkɛ kíaɛ yã́pii musuↄn kɛ: Zĩgↄ̃ gãliↄ ìↄ kↄ̃ lɛũkpakɛ mↄ ń mↄoɛ e wɛ̃ gɛ́ bↄlɛi, gãlipiↄ baade zĩgↄ̃ↄ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄo lɛɛ baasↄo mɛ̀ndosaiɛ (24.000). 
\p  
\v 2 Zadiɛli nɛ́ Yasↄbaũ mɛ́ mↄ sɛ̃́iadeↄ gãli dↄaana ũ.  
\v 3 Pɛlɛzi buiɛ. Ɔ̃mɛ zĩgↄ̃ↄ dↄaana píi gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ mↄ sɛ̃́ia guu. 
\p  
\v 4 Ahoa nɛ́ Dodai mɛ́ mↄ plaadeↄ gãli dↄaana ũ. Mikelo mɛ́ aà plaade ũ. 
\p  
\v 5 Sa'ona Yoiada nɛ́ Benaia mɛ́ mↄ àaↄ̃deↄ gãli dↄaana ũ.  
\v 6 Benaiapi mɛ́ nɛgↄ̃n gbɛ̃ↄn baakwiↄ dↄaana ũ lↄ. Aà nɛ́ Amizaba ku aà gãli guuɛ. 
\p  
\v 7 Yoabu dãuna Asaɛli mɛ́ mↄ síiↄ̃deↄ gãli dↄaana ũ. Kɛ́ à gà, ↄ̃ aà nɛ́ Zebadia gↄ̃̀ aà gɛ̃ɛ ũ. 
\p  
\v 8 Izala bui Samu mɛ́ mↄ sↄodeↄ gãli dↄaana ũ. 
\p  
\v 9 Tekoa gbɛ̃́ Ikesi nɛ́ Ila mɛ́ mↄ soolodeↄ gãli dↄaana ũ. 
\p  
\v 10 Ɛflaiũ bui Ɛlɛzi, Peloni gbɛ̃́ mɛ́ mↄ sopladeↄ gãli dↄaana ũ. 
\p  
\v 11 Zela bui Sibekai, Usa gbɛ̃́ mɛ́ mↄ swaaↄ̃deↄ gãli dↄaana ũ. 
\p  
\v 12 Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ bui Abiɛzɛɛ, Anato gbɛ̃́ mɛ́ mↄ kɛ̃okwideↄ gãli dↄaana ũ. 
\p  
\v 13 Zela bui Malai, Nɛtofa gbɛ̃́ mɛ́ mↄ kwideↄ gãli dↄaana ũ. 
\p  
\v 14 Ɛflaiũ bui Benaia, Pilatↄ̃ gbɛ̃́ mɛ́ mↄ kuɛdodeↄ gãli dↄaana ũ. 
\p  
\v 15 Ɔniɛli bui Ɛlɛdai, Nɛtofa gbɛ̃́ mɛ́ mↄ kuɛpladeↄ gãli dↄaana ũ. 
\s1 Isaili buiↄ dↄaanaↄ 
\q1  
\v 16 Isaili buiↄ kíaↄn kɛ: 
\q1 Lubɛni buiↄ kí Ɛliɛzɛɛ, Zikeli nɛ́, 
\q1 Simɛↄ buiↄ kí Sefatia, Maaka nɛ́, 
\q1  
\v 17 Levii buiↄ kí Asabia, Kɛmuɛ nɛ́, 
\q1 Aalona buiↄ kí Zadoki, 
\q1  
\v 18 Yudaↄ kí Ɛlihu, Davidi vĩ̀i, 
\q1 Isakaa buiↄ kí Ɔmɛli, Mikaila nɛ́, 
\q1  
\v 19 Zabulↄni buiↄ kí Isimaia, Obadia nɛ́, 
\q1 Nɛfatali buiↄ kí Yelimↄ, Azeliɛ nɛ́, 
\q1  
\v 20 Ɛflaiũ buiↄ kí Ozee, Azazia nɛ́, 
\q1 Manase bui pↄ́ kú bɛ'aɛ oiↄ kí Yoɛli, Pedaia nɛ́, 
\q1  
\v 21 Manase bui pↄ́ kú Galada bùsuuↄ kí Ido, Zakali nɛ́, 
\q1 Bɛ̃yãmɛɛ buiↄ kí Yaasiɛ, Abinɛɛ nɛ́, 
\q1  
\v 22 Dã buiↄ kí Azalɛli, Yeloaũ nɛ́. 
\q1 Isaili buiↄ kíaↄn we. 
\p  
\v 23 Davidi i gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kà wɛ̃̀ bao ge aai kaoↄ naoo, asa Dii mɛ̀ á tó Isailiↄ dasikũ lán saanaↄwaɛ.\f + \fr 27.23 \ft Daa 15.5, 22.17, 26.4\f* 
\v 24 Kɛ́ Zeluia nɛ́ Yoabu nà ń naoawa,\f + \fr 27.24 \ft 2Sam 24.1-15, 1Lad 21.1-14\f* i a midɛo. Naopi yã́i Lua pↄ fɛ̃̀i Isailiↄzi, ↄ̃ wì ń dasilɛ kɛ̃́ kí Davidi ladauo. 
\s1 Kía ìwaↄ 
\p  
\v 25 Adiɛli nɛ́ Azemavɛ mɛ́ kibɛ làasi gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. 
\p Uzia nɛ́ Yonatãa mɛ́ dↄ̃ pↄ́ kú bua ń mɛɛwiaↄ ń zↄ̃ɛwiaↄ ń gudↄ̃akĩiↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. 
\p  
\v 26 Kelubu nɛ́ Ɛzali mɛ́ buazĩkɛnaↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. 
\p  
\v 27 Lama gbɛ̃́ Simɛi mɛ́ vɛ̃ɛbudeↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. 
\p Sefã gbɛ̃́ Zabedi mɛ́ ziia ũ vɛ̃ɛbɛ ń vɛ̃ɛ kũ̀sũao yã́ musu. 
\p  
\v 28 Gɛdɛɛ gbɛ̃́ Baalanana mɛ́ kuliↄ ń kaadↄɛnliↄ zĩkɛnaↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. 
\p Yoasi mɛ́ ziia ũ kù nísi yã́ musu. 
\p  
\v 29 Salↄna gbɛ̃́ Sitelai mɛ́ Salↄna zùdãnaↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. 
\p Adelai nɛ́ Safata mɛ́ guzulɛ zùdãnaↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. 
\p  
\v 30 Isimaɛla bui Obili mɛ́ yiongodãnaↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. 
\p Mɛlↄnↄ gbɛ̃́ Yedeia mɛ́ zàa'ĩndãnaↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. 
\p  
\v 31 Ageli bui Yazizi mɛ́ sãↄ ń bleↄ dãnaↄ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ. Gbɛ̃́piↄá kí Davidi ziiaↄnɛ ḿpii. 
\p  
\v 32 Davidi desɛ̃ Yonatãaá lɛdamadeɛ. Aà wɛ́ zɛ̃a mɛ́ lakɛ̃naɛ. Aàpi ń Akemↄ nɛ́ Yeiɛlio mɛ́ Davidi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ gwana ũ.  
\v 33 Aitofɛli mɛ́ Davidi lɛdamade ũ. Aaki gbɛ̃́ Usai mɛ́ kí kwàasi ũ.  
\v 34 A gbɛa Benaia nɛ́ Yoiada ń Abiataao gↄ̃̀ Aitofɛli gɛ̃ɛ ũ. 
\p Yoabu mɛ́ kí zĩgↄ̃ↄ dↄaana ũ. 
\c 28  
\s1 Davidi Lua kpɛ́ dↄa zɛ́kalɛa Salomↄↄɛ 
\p  
\v 1 Davidi Isaili kíaↄ kã̀aa Yelusalɛũ píi, Isaili bui kíaↄ ń zĩgↄ̃ↄ dↄaana pↄ́ lɛ́ zĩkɛɛ̀ↄ, zĩgↄ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄoↄ dↄaanaↄ ń gbɛ̃ↄn basↄobasↄoↄ dↄaanaↄ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dɛ kía ń a nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ àizɛɛ ziia ũↄ ń a ìwaↄ ń a nɛgↄ̃naↄ ń a gↄ̃ gɛ̀bɛɛↄ píi.  
\v 2 Ɔ̃ kí Davidi fɛ̀lɛ zɛ̀ à mɛ̀: Ma gbɛ̃́ↄ, à swã́sɛmazi! Ma zɛò ma sↄ̃u mà kpɛdↄ Dii wá Lua bàakuawanↄ kpagolo pↄ́ dɛ aà gbadibↄ ũɛ, ↄ̃ ma sↄu mà ń a dↄao.  
\v 3 Ɔ̃ Lua òmɛɛ i kɛ mámɛ mà kpɛ́pi dↄɛo, asa zĩgↄ̃n ma ũ, ma gbɛ̃dɛ̀dɛ dasidasiɛ.  
\v 4 Ń beeo Dii wá Isailiↄ Lua ma sɛ ma bɛdeↄ guu, kɛ́ mapi ń ma buiↄ wàↄ dɛ Isailiↄ kía ũ gↄↄpiiɛ. À Yuda sɛ̀ yãa dↄaana ũ, ↄ̃ à ma bɛdeↄ sɛ̀ aà buiↄ guu. À kàaàgu, ↄ̃ à ma kpa Isailiↄ kía ũ.  
\v 5 Dii ma gba nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ dasi, ↄ̃ à Salomↄↄ sɛ̀ ń guu, à aà kpà kpala pↄ́ a dìlɛ Isailiↄnɛu.  
\v 6 A òmɛɛ à mɛ̀: N nɛ́ Salomↄↄ mɛ́ a kpɛdↄmɛɛ ń a uao, asa ma aà sɛ̀ ma nɛ́ ũɛ, míↄ dɛ aà mae ũ.  
\v 7 Tó a ma yãdilɛaↄ ń ma ikoyãↄ kũa lá a kũa gbãwa, má tó aà kpala àↄ ku gↄↄpiiɛ.\f + \fr 28.7 \ft 2Sam 7.5-16, 1Lad 17.4-14\f* 
\p  
\v 8 Ma gbɛ̃́ↄ, ma naɛ́ wá Luazi Isailiↄ bui pↄ́ kãaaa Dii aɛↄ wáa píi, àↄ tɛ Dii wá Lua yãdilɛaↄi ń laaio, kɛ́ àↄ ku bùsu maaɛ beeu, i gↄ̃ á buiↄnɛ e gↄↄpii.  
\v 9 Mpi sↄ̃, ma nɛ́ Salomↄↄ, ǹyↄ̃ ma Lua dↄ̃, ní zↄbleɛ̀ ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo teasisai, asa Dii ì wá sↄ̃ yↄɛ à wá làasooↄ ń yã́ pↄ́ wa zɛòↄ dↄ̃. Tó n aà kĩ́i wɛ̀ɛlɛ, ńyↄ̃ aà e. Tó n pãkpàaàzi sↄ̃, à gìnzin we e gↄↄpii.  
\v 10 Ǹyↄ̃ dↄ̃ kɛ́ Dii n sɛ ǹ kpɛdↄɛ a kúkĩi ũɛ. Sↄ̃dilɛ, ní zĩpi kɛ. 
\p  
\v 11 Ɔ̃ Davidi Lua kpɛ́ ń a kpɛɛlɛo taa pↄ́ a kɛ̀ taalau kpà a nɛ́ Salomↄↄwa ń a làasiↄ ń a kpɛa pↄ́ kú musu ń zĩ́lɛoↄ ń a duunkɛ̃makĩio.  
\v 12 Yã́ pↄ́ kú aà sↄ̃u Dii ua ń a kpɛ́nɛ pↄ́ liaaiↄ musu, à a taataa pↄ́ a kɛ̀ taalau kpàwà lↄ: Lua kpɛ́pi làasiↄ, pↄ́ pↄ́ wì Lua gba kálɛkĩiↄ,  
\v 13 Dii kpɛ́ zĩkɛbↄↄ ń lá wa sa'onaↄ ń Levii bui gãliↄ dilɛdilɛ aa Dii kpɛ́ zĩ kɛo.  
\v 14 À vua ń ã́nusu pↄ́ wa zĩkɛbↄpiↄpiò gbia dìlɛdilɛ:  
\v 15 Vua dauↄ ń a filiaↄ, ã́nusu dauↄ ń a filiaↄ,  
\v 16 vua táabũnu pↄ́ wì pɛ̃ɛ kálɛwàↄ, ã́nusu táabũnuↄ,  
\v 17 vua saaↄ, au'ɛlɛbↄ pↄ́ wa pì ń vuaoↄ, vua loↄ, vua taↄ, ã́nusu taↄ  
\v 18 ń tulaletikatɛakĩi pↄ́ wa pì ń vuao. À vua malaika gã̀sĩade pↄ́ an gã̀sĩa aↄ pooa Dii bàa kua ń Isailiↄ kpagoloa aà zĩkasↄ̃go ũ taa pↄ́ a kɛ̀ taalau kpàwà lↄ. 
\p  
\v 19 Davidi mɛ̀: Ma yã́piↄ taa dàlau píi, asa Dii gbãa mↄ̀a à ma wɛ́ kɛ̃̀mɛɛɛ.  
\v 20 Ɔ̃ Davidi ò a nɛ́ Salomↄↄɛ: Sↄ̃dilɛ, zĩpi kɛ ń wↄ́ↄo. Ńsu to vĩa n kũo. Ńsu bílikɛo, asa Dii ma Lua a pãkpanzio, a n to weo. Aↄ kunnↄɛ e ǹ gɛ ǹ kpɛ́ zĩpi midɛò.  
\v 21 Sa'onaↄ ń Levii buiↄ gãliↄ ku sↄu guu wà Dii kpɛ́pi zĩ kɛ, mɛ́ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa gↄ̃i vĩ mɛ́ an pↄ gbàↄ kunnↄ aa zĩpi kɛ. Gbɛ̃́pii ń ń kíaↄ aa n yãma. 
\c 29  
\s1 Gbadaa Lua kpɛ́ dↄa yã́ musu 
\p  
\v 1 Ɔ̃ kí Davidi ò gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kãaaaↄnɛ píi: Ma nɛ́ Salomↄↄ pↄ́ Lua aà sɛ̀piá ɛ̀waason bↄlↄnaɛ. Zĩpi zↄ̃ↄ, asa uapiá gbɛ̃nazĩna pↄ́ no, Dii Lua pↄ́ɛ.  
\v 2 Ma Lua kpɛ́pi dↄa sↄukɛ̀ maamaa ma gbãa lɛ́uɛ, ma vua kpà vua zĩ pↄ́ ũ ń ã́nusuo ã́nusu zĩ pↄ́ ũ ń mↄgotɛ̃o mↄgotɛ̃ zĩ pↄ́ ũ ń mↄsio mↄsi zĩ pↄ́ ũ ń lío lí zĩ pↄ́ ũ ń gbɛo gbɛ̀ zĩ pↄ́ ũ ń onisio ń tiikↄazio ń gbɛ̀ bɛɛɛde bui píio ń gbɛpuao.  
\v 3 Bee gbɛa lá ma Lua kpɛ́ yã́ kàmagu, vua ń ã́nusu àizɛɛ pↄ́ má vĩↄ, ↄ̃ má kpá ma Lua kpɛ́ pↄ́ ũ pↄ́ pↄ́ ma a sↄukɛ̀ↄ bàasi:  
\v 4 Ofii bùsu vua tↄnu basↄo ń ã́nusu tɛ̃ɛtɛ̃ɛo tↄnu ↄ̀aa do ń blao, kɛ́ wà kpa kpɛ́pi gĩↄwa a guu.  
\v 5 Vuaá vua zĩ pↄ́ɛ, ã́nusuá ã́nusu zĩ pↄ́ɛ ń zĩ pↄ́ gↄ̃ideↄ kɛↄ píi. Á démɛ zɛ̀ò gbã à kpa Diiwa sↄũsↄũi? 
\p  
\v 6 Ɔ̃ uabeleↄ ń Isaili bui kíaↄ ń zĩgↄ̃ gbɛ̃ↄn ↄ̀aasↄsↄoↄ dↄaanaↄ ń gbɛ̃ↄn basↄobasↄoↄ dↄaanaↄ ń kíapi ziiaↄ vua ń ã́nusuo kpà.  
\v 7 Aa vua kpà tↄnu baswaaↄ̃kwi (170) wà Lua kpɛ́pi zĩ kɛò ń ã́nusuo tↄnu ↄ̀aa do ń basoplao (340) ń mↄgotɛ̃o tↄnu ↄ̀aa àaↄ̃ ń kwio (610) ń mↄsio tↄnu ↄ̀aa gɛ̃o ń plao (3.400).  
\v 8 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ gbɛ̀ bɛɛɛdeↄ vĩↄ nà Geesↄ̃ bui Yeiɛliɛ a ↄzĩ Dii kpɛ́ làasiu.  
\v 9 Gbɛ̃́pii pↄ kɛ̀na pↄ́ pↄ́ wa kpàpi yã́ musu, asa aa kpà Diiwa ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndooɛ. Kí Davidi pↄ kɛ̀na maamaa,  
\v 10 ↄ̃ à Dii sáaukpà gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kãaaa weↄ wáa à mɛ̀: 
\q1 Ɛ̀fãaide Dii wá dezi Isaili Lua 
\q1 za asĩnizĩ e gↄↄpii! 
\q1  
\v 11 Dii, ḿmɛ ń zↄ̃ↄkɛ ń gbãao 
\q1 ń bɛɛɛo ń dɛnlao ń gawio vĩ, 
\q1 asa pↄ́ pↄ́ kú musu ń zĩ́lɛoↄá n pↄ́ɛ píi. 
\q1 Ḿmɛ ń kía ũ, 
\q1 ḿmɛ ń pↄ́pii mide ũ. 
\q1  
\v 12 Àizɛɛ ń bɛɛɛo ì bↄ n kĩ́iɛ, 
\q1 ni kible pↄ́piiwa. 
\q1 Iko ń gbãao ku n ↄzĩɛ, 
\q1 ń gbɛ̃́pii kã́fĩa zɛ́ vĩ, 
\q1 mɛ́ ń ń gbaa gbãa zɛ́ vĩ lↄ. 
\q1  
\v 13 Tiasa wá Lua, wálɛ n sáaukpa, 
\q1 wálɛ n tↄ́ bɛɛɛde bↄ. 
\m  
\v 14 Ée, dén ma ũ ge ma gbɛ̃́ↄ, kɛ́ wà gbasa pↄ́ kpama màai? Pↄ́pii ì bↄ n kĩ́iɛ. Pↄ́ pↄ́ wa kpàma bↄ̀ n ↄzĩɛ.  
\v 15 Wá dɛnɛ bↄ̀mↄↄ ũ, nibↄↄ ũ lán wá deziↄwaɛ. Wá kua dṹniau dɛ lán uenawa tãmaasaiɛ.  
\v 16 Dii wá Lua, pↄzↄ̃ↄ pↄ́ wá kpà n kpɛ́ dↄa yã́i, kɛ́ n tↄ́ pↄ́ a kua adoa e àↄ kuwà, apii bↄ̀ n ↄzĩɛ, n pↄ́ɛ.  
\v 17 Ma Lua, má dↄ̃ kɛ́ sↄ̃̀ tàasikanan n ũ, yãkɛa a zɛ́wa mɛ́ ì kangu. Ma pↄ́piↄ kpàma píi ń nↄ̀sɛpuaoɛ, ↄ̃ má è n gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kú laↄ pↄ́ kpàma ń pↄnao sↄ̃.  
\v 18 Dii wá deziↄ Ablahaũ ń Izaakio ń Isailio Lua, to n gbɛ̃́ↄ lí zɛò beewa ń sↄ̃ guu, ní tó an sↄ̃ àↄ kuma gↄↄpii.  
\v 19 Ma nɛ́ Salomↄↄ gba zɛ́ aàↄ n yãdilɛaↄ ń n ikoyãↄ kũa ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo, i n ↄtondↄkĩi gwa à zĩkɛwà píi, i n kpɛ́ pↄ́ ma a sↄukɛ̀ dↄ. 
\p  
\v 20 Ɔ̃ Davidi ò gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kãaaa weↄnɛ: À Dii á Lua sáaukpa! Ɔ̃ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kãaaa weↄ Dii ń deziↄ Lua sáaukpà, aa mipɛ̀lɛ aa kùlɛ Diiɛ, aa kùlɛ kíaɛ lↄ. 
\s1 Salomↄↄ kpaa kía ũ 
\p  
\v 21 Kɛ́ gu dↄ̀ aa sa'ò Diiwa. Aa sa pↄ́ wì a pↄ́ kátɛu à tɛ́kũ òwà ń zuswanaↄ mɛ̀n ↄ̀aa sↄo ń sãsakaoↄ mɛ̀n ↄ̀aa sↄo ń sãsa bↄlↄnaↄ mɛ̀n ↄ̀aa sↄo. Aa vɛ̃ɛ ɛ̀lɛwà aa sáaukpa sa'òwà dúuduu Isaili píi pↄ́ ũ.  
\v 22 Gↄↄ bee aa pↄblè aa vɛ̃ɛmì Dii aɛ ń pↄna zↄ̃ↄo. 
\p Ɔ̃ aa Davidi nɛ́ Salomↄↄ kpaa kía ũ gbãa kã̀fĩ.\f + \fr 29.22 \ft 1Lad 23.1\f* Aa aà kpà kía ũ Dii aɛ sa, ↄ̃ aa Zadoki dìlɛ sa'onkia ũ.  
\v 23 Ɔ̃ Salomↄↄ zↄ̃̀lɛ kpalau a mae gbɛu kía pↄ́ Dii kpà ũ.\f + \fr 29.23 \ft 1Kia 2.12\f* À gwea è mɛ́ Isaili bui píi misìilɛɛ̀.  
\v 24 Kíaↄ ń nɛgↄ̃naↄ ń kí Davidi nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ píi mikpà kí Salomↄↄwa.  
\v 25 Dii tò Salomↄↄ zↄ̃ↄkɛ kã̀fĩ maamaa, Isaili bui píi wɛ́ è. Dii kíakɛgawi kpàwà, Isailiↄ kía pↄ́ dↄaaaɛ̀ↄ, an kee i kaaàwao. 
\s1 Davidi gaa 
\p  
\v 26 Yɛse nɛ́ Davidiá Isaili buiↄ píi kíaɛ.  
\v 27 À kɛ̀ kpalau wɛ̃̀ blaɛ, Hɛblↄ̃ wɛ̃̀ sopla, Yelusalɛũ sↄ̃ wɛ̃̀ baakwi ń àaↄ̃o.\f + \fr 29.27 \ft 2Sam 5.4-5\f* 
\v 28 À zikũ̀ táotaoɛ, ↄ̃ à gà. Ɔdeɛ mɛ́ a bɛɛɛ vĩ. Ɔ̃ aà nɛ́ Salomↄↄ zↄ̃̀lɛ aà gbɛu.  
\v 29 Kí Davidi yãkɛaↄ ku gu'ena Samuɛli taalau ń ãnabi Natã láo ń gu'ena Gada láo za a daalɛawa e a midɛawa,  
\v 30 aà kpalablea yã́ↄ ń aà nɛgↄ̃nkɛyãↄ ń yã́ pↄ́ aà lèↄ ń yã́ pↄ́ Isailiↄ ń bùsu pↄ́ liaai kíaↄ lèↄ.